2
00:00:03,860 --> 00:00:07,530
当时我就在那里 面对赛伦盖提
So there I was, face to face with the biggest,

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:10,400
…最大最凶猛的花豹，然后…
meanest leopard on this side of the Serengeti. And...

4
00:00:10,470 --> 00:00:13,530
你大吼一声 吓得他的豹纹掉满地
You roared so loud, his spots flew clean off.

5
00:00:13,610 --> 00:00:15,970
爸，这故事我听过N遍了
Dad, I've heard this like a billion times.

6
00:00:16,040 --> 00:00:19,010
你听我说过 有一次我把奸笑土狼
Do you know the one where I made the laughing hyenas...

7
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:21,070
…弄哭，对吧？  听过了
Cry? Yep.

8
00:00:21,150 --> 00:00:23,010
我被鳄鱼攻击？  爸
The croc attack?  Dad.

9
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:24,980
好啦，我再想想看
OK. Think.

10
00:00:25,050 --> 00:00:27,210
好吧，尽管想吧
Yeah, you do that.

11
00:00:27,290 --> 00:00:29,310
我想到了，聪明小子
All right, Mr. Smart Guy,

12
00:00:29,390 --> 00:00:32,190
你一定没听过这个故事
here's one I know you haven't heard.

13
00:00:33,260 --> 00:00:37,720
故事发生在一个小地方 我称它
It all started in the little place I like to call...

14
00:00:39,900 --> 00:00:41,130
…大草原
...the wild.

15
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:42,570
【野蛮任务】

16
00:00:43,540 --> 00:00:46,670
他们是大草原 跑得最快的牛羚
They were the fastest wildebeests on the savannah.

17
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:49,970
他们真的超快的
We're talking fast.

18
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:53,140
其他的狮子早在 几小时前就放弃猎捕他们
All the other lions had given up the hunt hours ago,

19
00:00:53,210 --> 00:00:54,980
除了你老爸
except your old man.

20
00:00:55,050 --> 00:00:57,780
还好我知道一条捷径
Fortunately, I knew a short cut.

21
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:06,160
我自以为困住他们了 但尘沙散去
I thought I had 'em. Until the dust cleared.

22
00:01:07,430 --> 00:01:09,090
才发现中了牛羚的圈套
Classic wildebeest trap.

23
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:11,090
你怎么办？
So, what did you do next?

24
00:01:11,170 --> 00:01:12,830
我怎么办？  对啊
What did I do?  Yeah.

25
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:16,390
我大吼一声
That's when I gave them the roar.

26
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:33,420
就这样？  好戏在后头
That's it?  Hold on a sec.

27
00:01:33,490 --> 00:01:36,650
我以为这样就搞定了
I only thought it was over.

28
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:41,090
不过他们有一项秘密武器
But they had a secret weapon.

29
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:44,100
我从没见过那么大的牛羚
He was the biggest wildebeest I've ever seen.

30
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:47,030
足足有四公尺高  才四公尺？
He was 14 feet tall!  Fourteen?

31
00:01:47,100 --> 00:01:52,600
我是说四百公尺 又三十公分
I meant 1,401 feet tall!

32
00:01:52,670 --> 00:01:54,570
酷毙了
Cool.

33
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:57,630
而且他还有两只…不，四只
And he had two... No, four

34
00:01:57,710 --> 00:02:00,650
最巨大的牛羚角
of the biggest horns I'd ever seen.

35
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:04,850
哇塞  他喷出红色的气焰
Whoa!  His breath was red hot!

36
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,510
我是说绿色的啦
I mean, green.

37
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:08,890
而且他超讨厌这鬼地方
And he hated the environment.

38
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:11,930
我知道要打败他 一定要激发我内心深处
To pull this off, I knew I was gonna have to dig deep,

39
00:02:11,990 --> 00:02:13,980
前所未有的勇气
deeper than I ever had before.

40
00:02:14,060 --> 00:02:16,000
于是我强忍住恐惧
So I swallowed my fear,

41
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:18,260
深深地吸了一口气
sucked in the biggest breath I could.

42
00:02:18,330 --> 00:02:19,660
爸，我准备好了
Dad, I'm ready!

43
00:02:19,730 --> 00:02:20,930
你行吗？  我行！
You got it?  I got it!

44
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,660
我行！  那就让他好看吧
I got it!  Well, let him have it!

45
00:02:22,740 --> 00:02:25,360
大声吼吧，儿子
Roar, son!

46
00:02:40,690 --> 00:02:42,620
（纽约市立动物园）

47
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:51,730
每次都是这样
Story of my life.

48
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:55,360
你的吼声吓跑一群牛羚 我的吼声只会逗小朋友笑
Your roar stops a herd of wildebeests. Mine makes the babies laugh.

49
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,560
别气馁，你这次好多了
Hey, come on. That was much better.

50
00:02:57,640 --> 00:03:00,900
我是说真的 降了半个八度
I'm serious! It dropped half an octave.

51
00:03:00,970 --> 00:03:05,240
你再降半个八度 我都会被你吓到皮皮挫
It dropped half an octave. And it sure scared me.

52
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:08,710
让我全身的毛都竖起来  才怪咧，爸
Made my hair stand up on end.  Yeah, right, Dad.

53
00:03:08,780 --> 00:03:12,220
好吧，再练一次  今天就练到这里
OK. Let's take it from the top.  I'm done for today.

54
00:03:12,290 --> 00:03:14,780
别这样嘛，再来一次 就差这么一点点
Come on, come on, one more. You were so close.

55
00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:16,580
也许是技术性问题
Maybe it's something technical.

56
00:03:16,660 --> 00:03:19,720
也许你的嘴巴张得不够大 要像这样子
Maybe you're not opening your mouth wide enough. Like this.

57
00:03:19,790 --> 00:03:23,460
爸，多谢你的技术指导
Dad, thanks for the technical help,

58
00:03:23,530 --> 00:03:26,860
不过你要我吼得跟你一样 就得带我到真正的大草原
but if you wanted me to roar like you, you'd take me to the wild.

59
00:03:26,930 --> 00:03:30,730
你有没有搞错？ 咱们在这里应有尽有
Hold on a second. We've got everything we could ever want here.

60
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,800
生活很享受 每天照三顿吃饭
Great lifestyle, three squares a day.

61
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:34,170
超无聊的  无聊？
It's boring.  Boring?

62
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,540
我在这里学不会狮吼  雷恩
I'll never learn how to roar here.  Ryan.

63
00:03:36,610 --> 00:03:39,010
不过你放心 我终于想出办法
But don't worry. I finally figured out

64
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:41,310
怎么去野外  真的吗？
how we can get to the wild.  You did?

65
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:44,080
鸽子说那些绿色箱子 都是运到那里
The pigeons say those green boxes go there.

66
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:46,920
那些箱子不吉利 离它们远一点
Those boxes are bad news. Stay away.

67
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:49,580
可是，爸…  我知道你很郁卒
But, Dad...  I know you're frustrated,

68
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:52,350
不过狮子在这里 也能学会大吼
but a lion finds his roar...  Here.

69
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:55,450
爸，你老是说这种话哄我
I'm so tired of hearing that, Dad!

70
00:03:55,530 --> 00:03:56,830
有一只老鼠
It's a rat!

71
00:03:56,900 --> 00:03:58,630
快把那只老鼠赶走
Get that rat off my baby!

72
00:03:58,700 --> 00:04:00,000
老鼠？
A rat?

73
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:02,790
你好
Hello!

74
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,460
好好玩的老鼠哦
Silly, silly rat.

75
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:08,970
老鼠才不喜欢这种手环，小姐 你这小…
Rats do not got bling like this, lady.  You little...!

76
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:18,640
那是我见过最丑的小贝比
Lastly, that is the ugliest baby I've ever seen!

77
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:21,380
斑尼，你偷小贝比的糖果？
Benny, stealing candy from a baby?

78
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:26,490
别说得这么难听 我只是怕他会蛀牙
Stealing is such a strong word. I prefer "liberating."

79
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:29,360
小鬼，我听到你的吼声 又降了…
Hey, kid, heard the roar. Down another...

80
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:32,560
八度  八度！
Octave.  Octave!

81
00:04:32,870 --> 00:04:36,530
你要来替我跟你爸加油 看我们连续第五次夺下
You ready to cheer me and your old man as we capture our fifth straight

82
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:39,940
冰龟赛冠军吗？
turtle-curling title?

83
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:43,910
我根本就不会吼叫 你怎么知道我在加油？
I can't even roar. How would you even know I'm there?

84
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:46,540
你真的觉得降了八度吗？
So, you really think it dropped an octave?

85
00:04:46,610 --> 00:04:48,840
当然罗
Absolutely.

86
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:52,940
八度到底是什么东东？  我听见了
What the heck is an octave?  I heard that.

87
00:04:54,890 --> 00:04:58,880
兔子  胆固醇太高，我吃坚果
Rabbit.  Cholesterol. I'll stick with the nuts.

88
00:04:59,860 --> 00:05:01,990
我不知道他的问题出在哪儿
I don't know what his problem is, Benny.

89
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:05,160
他都已经11岁了 可是吼声还停在9岁的程度
He's 11, but he's still roaring at a nine-year-old level.

90
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:07,390
山大王，帮个忙
Little help here, Sammy?

91
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:12,530
你知道吗？ 也许你的标准太高了
You know what? Maybe you're setting the bar too high,

92
00:05:12,610 --> 00:05:15,130
你老是提那些山大王 在大草原的英勇故事
with all those stories about Samson the Wild.

93
00:05:15,210 --> 00:05:19,510
他超爱听那些故事的 对他是一种激励耶
Hey, he's always loved those stories! They inspire him.

94
00:05:19,580 --> 00:05:23,850
好啦，我不想跟你吵 我怕你拿我的尾巴当牙线
OK. I'm not gonna argue with someone who can use my tail as dental floss.

95
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:27,250
你的牙缝有渣渣  哪里？
You got something right there.  Where?

96
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:29,920
不对，另一边  这边？
No, no, other side.  Here?

97
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:32,080
抱歉，斑尼  弄出来了
Sorry, Benny.  You got it.

98
00:05:32,290 --> 00:05:33,690
亲爱的大朋友小朋友
Attention, friends.

99
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:37,130
别忘了到礼品店购买 全国最抢手的填充玩偶
Stop by the gift shop and get the most popular plush in America:

100
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:39,130
尼啾无尾熊 会说「我喜欢你」
Nigel, the "l-Like-You" Koala.

101
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:42,600
瞧，亲爱的，它会说话耶  我是小可爱，我爱你
Look, honey! The crazy thing talks!  I'm so cuddly! I like you!

102
00:05:42,670 --> 00:05:46,870
没错，他超可爱的 更赞的是，他喜欢你
That's right. He's so cuddly. And better yet, he likes you.

103
00:05:50,910 --> 00:05:52,470
终于…
Finally.

104
00:05:52,550 --> 00:05:55,810
动物园就快是咱们的天下了 倒数三秒
And the zoo will officially be ours in T-minus three...

105
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:57,080
（纽约市立动物园）
...two...

106
00:05:57,150 --> 00:05:58,310
两秒
...and showtime!

107
00:05:58,390 --> 00:06:01,010
好戏上场！

108
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,820
我来也
Here I come!

109
00:06:05,890 --> 00:06:07,380
谁把栅栏放在这儿？
Who put that bar there?

110
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,490
好痒哦
That tickles!

111
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,400
我有啦  才没有
Did too!  Did not!

112
00:06:18,470 --> 00:06:19,700
我有  才没有
Did too!  Did not!

113
00:06:19,770 --> 00:06:21,000
给我让开，懒惰鬼
Out of my way, ya bum!

114
00:06:21,070 --> 00:06:23,010
那个讨厌的无尾熊在哪里
There's that moth-eaten koala!

115
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:26,570
我跟你们这些火鹤说过一百遍 给我滚开
I've told you flamingos a hundred times, walk.

116
00:06:26,650 --> 00:06:28,580
我要签名  不行
How about an autograph?!  Don't...

117
00:06:28,650 --> 00:06:31,050
各位鸟兄弟 帮我找他背后的拉线
Birds! Find the string on his back!

118
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:34,210
你今天的心情很好耶  各位
So you're havin' a really nice day!  Guys.

119
00:06:34,490 --> 00:06:36,290
别碰我的副队长
Off my co-captain, now.

120
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,820
抱歉，山大王
Sorry, Samson.

121
00:06:39,660 --> 00:06:41,290
一点都不痛
That didn't hurt.

122
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:45,350
我差点忘了告诉你 我终于要约BJ出去
I almost forgot to tell you. I'm gonna ask Bridget out finally.

123
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:50,100
等一下，罗密欧 你是只松鼠，她可是…
Slow down, Romeo. You are a squirrel and she is...

124
00:06:50,170 --> 00:06:51,160
跟我很速配，对吧？
Perfect, right?

125
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:55,470
我懂你的意思啦 相信我，我的眼睛是雪亮的
Look, I know what you're sayin'. Believe me, I got my eyes wide open.

126
00:06:55,540 --> 00:06:57,940
走路不长眼啊，你这大…
Watch where you're goin', you big...!

127
00:07:09,060 --> 00:07:11,680
别盯着我的斑点看，斑尼 我的眼睛在上面
BJ Bridget.

128
00:07:09,060 --> 00:07:11,680
Don't stare at my spots, Benny. My eyes are up here.

129
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:18,020
当然了，歹势哦 这是送你的，小亲亲
Of course. I'm so sorry. Oh, this is for you, honey.

130
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:20,360
可以戴在左脚上面
It goes around your left hoof.

131
00:07:20,430 --> 00:07:22,160
你从垃圾堆捡来的吗？
Did you get that out of the trash?

132
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,500
就是了，你这捡垃圾的脏鬼
You did! You trash-picker!

133
00:07:25,570 --> 00:07:28,130
我不是捡垃圾 我是在做资源回收
I'm not a trash-picker. I'm a recycler.

134
00:07:28,210 --> 00:07:31,180
这样比较浪漫，不是吗？
That's a lot more romantic. Isn't it?

135
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,870
浪漫？  山大王，过来
Romantic?  Sam, come here.

136
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:35,410
浪漫？ 别跟我谈浪漫，斑尼
Romantic? Don't mention romance to me, Benny.

137
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,920
我从来没有交过男朋友  那正好
I've never had a boyfriend.  That settles it.

138
00:07:37,980 --> 00:07:40,380
我自愿当你的第一位男友
I accept the job... of boyfriend number one.

139
00:07:40,450 --> 00:07:43,250
斑尼，只有雌性圆网蜘蛛
Benny, only the female orb-weaver spider

140
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,720
才会和比她小二十倍的 男生约会
will date a male one-twentieth her size.

141
00:07:45,790 --> 00:07:48,260
我还是有希望  然后她会吃了他
So there's hope!  And then she eats him.

142
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,890
至少他死得很快乐
But at least he dies happy.

143
00:07:55,670 --> 00:07:57,190
兄弟，我们去找雷恩
Let's get Ryan, dude!

144
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:59,930
兄弟，我们真有默契耶
Dude! We said that at the same time!

145
00:08:00,010 --> 00:08:01,940
兄弟
Dude.

146
00:08:08,150 --> 00:08:09,950
喂，雷恩
Hey! Hey, Ryan.

147
00:08:10,620 --> 00:08:14,420
我要去参加比赛了 待会见，好吗？
Listen, I'm headin' down to the game. I'm gonna see you there, right?

148
00:08:14,490 --> 00:08:17,290
来嘛，雷恩，我们需要你 你是我们的头号粉丝
Come on, Ryan. We need you. You're our biggest fan.

149
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:22,450
山大王 我才是你的头号粉丝
Yo, Samson! I'm your number one fan, man!

150
00:08:22,530 --> 00:08:25,460
谢了，老兄 我也是你的粉丝
Thanks, man. Right back at ya!

151
00:08:25,530 --> 00:08:27,690
爸，你刚才要说什么？
You were saying, Dad?

152
00:08:27,770 --> 00:08:30,600
听着，今天下午我只是想…
Listen. About this afternoon, I was just trying...

153
00:08:30,670 --> 00:08:33,970
爸，没事啦 我会去看你比赛，好吗？
Dad, fine. I'll go to your game, all right?

154
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:39,540
好吧，那就…待会见罗
OK. I'll... see you there, then.

155
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:51,210
来吧，兄弟
Come on, dude.

156
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:53,950
兄弟  你猜谁来了？
Dude.  Guess who's here?

157
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:56,190
伊斯、杜克
Eze. Duke.

158
00:08:56,260 --> 00:08:58,320
讨厌，他每次都猜对
Man, he always guesses.

159
00:08:58,400 --> 00:09:02,200
大家都去看比赛 我们可以趁机追捕瞪羚
We're gonna stalk the gazelles while everybody's at the game.

160
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:06,170
你来不来？  来嘛，小兄弟
You in?  Let's go, bro!

161
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,710
雷恩小兵
The Ryanator.

162
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:11,000
我这就下来
I'm comin' down.

163
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:14,740
鱼头！ 冷冻鱼头特价大拍卖！
Fish heads! Get your ice-cold fish heads!

164
00:09:14,820 --> 00:09:16,250
免费赠送鱼眼哦
Now eyeball-free!

165
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:19,410
冰龟锦标赛进入最后一局
We're into the final period of the curling championships

166
00:09:19,490 --> 00:09:21,820
轮到企鹅队上场 维特要丢了
and the penguins are up. Here comes Victor.

167
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:25,190
好样的
What a beauty!

168
00:09:25,260 --> 00:09:26,320
好耶，快刷呀
Yeah, sweep!

169
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:30,630
直接朝着红心滑过去 这次很可能直接命中目标
Heading straight for the bull's-eye! This could be it, folks!

170
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:32,630
命中目标  好耶！
Bo-wango!  Yes!

171
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:35,460
好耶  这下很难打败他们了
Oh, yeah!  That's gonna be tough to beat.

172
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:37,030
什么？「很难打败他们」？
What? "Tough to beat"?

173
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:39,500
这才是我们最爱的挑战 对吧，大伙儿？
That's just the way we like it, right, guys?

174
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:44,340
我不敢相信
I can't believe this!

175
00:09:44,410 --> 00:09:48,140
如果输了，我就要拧断 我的脑袋，还有你的
If we lose, I'm gonna rip my head off! And yours!

176
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:50,510
咱们可不能输给那群 不会飞的笨鸟
We cannot lose to flightless birds!

177
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:54,850
拜托，咱们不会输了这场比赛
Whoa, whoa. No one is losing anything around here.

178
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:57,320
只要大家保持专注
As long as we stay focused.

179
00:09:57,390 --> 00:10:00,150
对了，有人看到雷恩吗？  我知道了
By the way, has anyone seen Ryan?  Oh! I know!

180
00:10:00,230 --> 00:10:03,320
也许他活在老爸阴影下 心情很郁卒
Maybe he's sulking 'cause he lives in his father's shadow

181
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:05,520
而且他的吼声和女生一样逊
and he roars like a schoolgirl.

182
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,530
多谢了，赖瑞  不客气
Thanks, Lar.  You betcha!

183
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:10,700
尼啾，在我的玩偶上面签名
Nigel! Nigel! Will you sign my dolly?

184
00:10:10,770 --> 00:10:13,300
不要吧  尼啾，别理他们
Not again.  Nigel, ignore them.

185
00:10:13,370 --> 00:10:14,970
我是小可爱，我爱你
I'm so cuddly! I like you!

186
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:18,440
你超可爱的，我们都爱你  够了，我一点都不可爱
You're so cuddly! We love you!  That's it! I am not cuddly!

187
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:21,880
我是来自伦敦街头 在道上混的丛林狠角色
I'm a vicious jungle animal from the streets of London!

188
00:10:21,950 --> 00:10:24,080
怕了吧  抓住他！抓住他！
Fear me!  Get him! Get him! Get him!

189
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:27,810
救命啊！  美眉们，把他放下来
Help me!  Girls! Put him down.

190
00:10:27,890 --> 00:10:29,080
我不是玩偶
I am not a doll!

191
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:31,450
软绵绵的小屁屁  别摸我的屁股
Cushy tushy!  Leave my bum alone!

192
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:34,220
尼啾，别碰我的女朋友
Nigel! Get your paws off my girlfriend!

193
00:10:34,290 --> 00:10:36,260
斑尼，我又不是你的女朋友
Benny, I am not your girlfriend!

194
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:42,060
好棒的一天哦
Really nice day!

195
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:45,970
山大王队是怎么了？ 逊毙了
What is up with Samson's team tonight? Brutal!

196
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,370
斑尼？
Benny?

197
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,640
天啊，谁会口对口人工呼吸？
Oh, my gosh! Who knows mouth-to-mouth?

198
00:10:49,710 --> 00:10:50,970
我会
I do!

199
00:10:52,180 --> 00:10:53,410
这算什么？
What was that?

200
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:55,880
你每天所需的斑尼维他命 宝贝儿
Just your daily dose of vitamin Benny, baby.

201
00:10:55,950 --> 00:10:58,180
给我滚开  我是小可爱，我爱你
Get off my nose.  I'm so cuddly, I like you!

202
00:10:58,250 --> 00:11:00,080
给我闭嘴  你好，老兄
Stop saying that!  G'day, mate!

203
00:11:00,150 --> 00:11:01,850
我要跳罗
Cannonball!

204
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:06,190
明年我只要当教练
Next year, I should just coach.

205
00:11:08,060 --> 00:11:09,790
你看，汤氏瞪羚
Check it. The Thomson gazelle.

206
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:12,660
4点5秒内就能加速到 时速80公里
Zero to 50 in four-point-five seconds.

207
00:11:12,730 --> 00:11:16,760
速度最快的逃命高手  无人可比
The ultimate fleeing machine.  There is no substitute.

208
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:20,140
咱们靠近一点看看这群瘦子
Let's get a closer look at these slim jims.

209
00:11:20,210 --> 00:11:22,700
这样好吗？  当然好
Shall we?  I think we shall.

210
00:11:22,780 --> 00:11:24,770
也许应该去看比赛
Maybe we should just go to the game.

211
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:28,110
你不是想当野蛮动物吗？  你老爸也追过瞪羚
I thought you wanted to be wild.  Your dad chased gazelles.

212
00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:31,170
如果他在我们这年纪 一定会跟我们一起大玩特玩
Yeah, if he were our age, he would so be rockin' out with us.

213
00:11:31,250 --> 00:11:34,220
他一定会把他们扑倒 把他们当成…
He'd be in there, runnin' 'em down like they were...

214
00:11:34,290 --> 00:11:37,450
瞪羚  没错，瞪羚之类的
Gazelles.  Yeah, gazelles or somethin'.

215
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,620
准备好了吗？
Ready, man?

216
00:11:39,430 --> 00:11:40,420
最好还是不要啦
We'd better not.

217
00:11:40,490 --> 00:11:43,090
干吗？你打算阻止我们吗？
Oh, yeah? Are you gonna stop us?

218
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:45,960
大伙儿  上吧
Guys, guys.  Here we go!

219
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:48,500
整场比赛的输赢 就看这一次
The whole series comes down to this throw!

220
00:11:48,570 --> 00:11:51,500
我俩没有明天 不是你死就是我亡
There's no tomorrow! It's do or die!

221
00:11:51,570 --> 00:11:53,060
你们懂我的意思啦
Ya know what I mean.

222
00:11:53,140 --> 00:11:56,130
大伙儿，我知道我们落后 不过我们会反败为胜
Guys, I know we're down, but we're gonna pull this out

223
00:11:56,210 --> 00:11:58,110
因为我们要使出
'cause we're gonna use...

224
00:11:58,180 --> 00:12:00,740
…秘密绝招  秘密绝招！
...the secret play.  The secret play!

225
00:12:00,810 --> 00:12:05,010
大伙儿，猜怎么着？ 我们要用秘密绝招耶
Hey, everybody, guess what? We're gonna use the secret play!

226
00:12:05,090 --> 00:12:07,110
赖瑞 秘密绝招最重要的一件事
Larry, the first part of the secret play

227
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:08,750
就是要保守秘密
is keeping it secret.

228
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:10,150
好啦  跟着我
OK.  Follow my lead.

229
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:12,850
大家要加倍努力
I'm going to need a double effort from everybody.

230
00:12:12,930 --> 00:12:15,690
没问题，队长 三倍努力都行
Absolutely, captain. Triple effort if you want, sir.

231
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:18,320
很好，预备…  散开
Good. Ready, and...  Break!

232
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:20,430
安静
Quiet.

233
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:22,990
我数到三 一、二…
On three, dude. One, two...

234
00:12:23,070 --> 00:12:24,470
不！
No!

235
00:12:33,710 --> 00:12:36,410
这下被你搞砸了，雷恩
Now you did it, Ryan.

236
00:12:37,420 --> 00:12:39,010
你够狠吗，阿诺？
Feelin' mean, Donald?

237
00:12:39,090 --> 00:12:40,380
放马过来吧
Bring it on!

238
00:12:40,450 --> 00:12:42,820
各位，山大王的压力很大
Folks, there's pressure on the big guy!

239
00:12:42,890 --> 00:12:44,980
准备好了吗，BJ？  好了
Ready, Bridget?  Ready.

240
00:12:45,060 --> 00:12:47,550
斑尼，你呢？  准备好了
Ready, Benny?  Ready!

241
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:53,000
山大王，可惜你那小鬼 没来看你输得惨兮兮
Samson, it's a shame your little brat isn't here to see you lose.

242
00:12:53,070 --> 00:12:56,660
我撑不下去了
I can't... hold it!

243
00:12:56,740 --> 00:12:59,800
噢，不，你在干吗？
Oh, no! What are you doin'?

244
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:05,370
山大王要丢了 大家看看他有多猛
And here comes Samson. Look at that guy.

245
00:13:05,450 --> 00:13:07,410
他是不是帅呆了？
Is he a beauty or what?

246
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:09,540
赖瑞！BJ！快刷！
Larry! Bridget! Sweep!

247
00:13:09,620 --> 00:13:11,210
真有一套
What a recovery!

248
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:14,250
他派BJ和赖瑞上场
He's sendin' in Bridget and Larry to do the job!

249
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:16,410
刷快点，赖瑞！ 快刷，快刷！
Sweep faster, Larry! Sweep, sweep!

250
00:13:16,490 --> 00:13:18,250
我在刷呀  加油
I am!  Come on, man!

251
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,760
企鹅队派出他们的王牌维特
Team Penguin is sending their ace, Victor...

252
00:13:20,830 --> 00:13:23,490
小心，维特  你自己才要小心
Watch it, Victor!  Watch it yourself, see?

253
00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:26,690
尼啾，情况如何？
Nigel, how are we looking?

254
00:13:26,770 --> 00:13:29,830
大伙儿，情况不妙  刷刷刷，刷刷刷
This could be trouble, folks!  Sweep, sweep, sweep.

255
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:32,240
这是作弊，你们死定了
This is cheating and you will die for this.

256
00:13:32,310 --> 00:13:34,030
我听不到，尼啾
I can't hear you, Nigel.

257
00:13:34,110 --> 00:13:36,700
往左一点点
Move left a bit...

258
00:13:37,210 --> 00:13:39,580
很好，往左然后用力一击
OK. Move left and hit!

259
00:13:39,650 --> 00:13:43,280
赖瑞，不要  大力一挥
Larry, no!  Tallyho!

260
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,080
好漂亮的动作
What a move!

261
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:53,760
各位，再过几寸 这将是冰龟大赛
Folks, we are inches away from the greatest upset

262
00:13:53,830 --> 00:13:56,090
史上最精采的反败为胜
in turtle-curling history!

263
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:58,630
糟了，我不敢相信我看到的  不！
Oh, no! I can't believe my eyes!  No!

264
00:13:58,700 --> 00:14:00,720
看来山大王凸槌了
Looks like Samson might have choked!

265
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,930
漂亮  好耶
Nice!  Yes!

266
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,700
真是不可思议
Unbelievable!

267
00:14:06,770 --> 00:14:09,970
山大王和他的队友 一举夺下冠军
Samson and his team have clinched the title!

268
00:14:10,040 --> 00:14:12,880
等等，我话说的太早了  搞什么鬼？
No, wait! I've called it too soon!  What the heck?

269
00:14:12,950 --> 00:14:16,940
企鹅队赢了 他们首度夺下冠军
The penguins have done it! They're zoo champs for the first time!

270
00:14:17,020 --> 00:14:20,580
群兽逃窜？群兽逃窜！
Stampede? Stampede!

271
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:24,190
拜托，停下来
Please! Stop!

272
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,060
小心
Watch out!

273
00:14:42,540 --> 00:14:44,980
兄弟，我们被逮到了
Dude. Busted.

274
00:14:45,040 --> 00:14:46,770
事情大条了
Catastrophic.

275
00:14:46,850 --> 00:14:48,910
我说过会来看比赛
Told you I'd come to the game.

276
00:14:48,980 --> 00:14:50,420
你觉得这样很好玩？
You think this is funny?

277
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:52,780
你差点把动物园的动物都害惨
You just endangered everyone in the zoo!

278
00:14:52,850 --> 00:14:54,320
抱歉  你为什么道歉？
I'm sorry.  For what?

279
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:56,980
为了追赶瞪羚 还是害我们输掉比赛？
Chasing the gazelles or costing us the game?

280
00:14:57,060 --> 00:14:59,080
你只会躲在树上垂头丧气
All you do is sit up in your tree and sulk.

281
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:01,130
如果你…  你到底怎么啦？
If you just...  What's the problem?

282
00:15:01,190 --> 00:15:03,090
只因为你不会吼吗？
Is all this because you can't roar?

283
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:08,630
雷恩，我不是故意的
Ryan, I didn't mean that.

284
00:15:08,700 --> 00:15:11,170
你知道我为什么躲在树上 成天垂头丧气吗？
Know what I'm doing when I'm sulking in my tree?

285
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:14,800
我真希望万兽之王 山大王不是我老爸
I'm thinking how great it would be if Samson the Wild wasn't my father.

286
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:17,370
雷恩，我不是…
Ryan, I didn't...

287
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:20,310
这样大家就不会瞧不起 我这个逊脚雷恩
'Cause it would make being Ryan the Lame a lot easier.

288
00:15:20,380 --> 00:15:22,210
雷恩，对不起
Ryan, I'm sorry.

289
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:25,770
雷恩，求求你
Ryan! Please don't...

290
00:15:25,850 --> 00:15:27,720
…别走
...leave.

291
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:31,120
拜了，雷恩 多谢你来看比赛
Bye, Ryan! Thanks for coming to the game.

292
00:15:31,190 --> 00:15:33,990
你还怕他不来
And you were worried he wouldn't show up.

293
00:15:38,770 --> 00:15:42,060
真是的 没有人肯听松鼠的话
Not good. No one listens to the squirrel.

294
00:15:44,140 --> 00:15:46,610
我不知道该怎么办，斑尼
I don't know what to do anymore, Benny.

295
00:15:46,670 --> 00:15:49,940
我什么方法都试过了  真的吗？
I've tried everything.  Everything?

296
00:15:50,010 --> 00:15:53,310
你什么方法都试过？  你想说什么？
You tried everything?  What are you saying?

297
00:15:53,380 --> 00:15:55,900
我只想说你要告诉他实话
I'm saying you have to tell him the truth.

298
00:15:56,980 --> 00:15:58,920
我不能说实话，斑尼
I don't think I could do that, Benny.

299
00:15:58,990 --> 00:16:00,580
我是说…
I mean...

300
00:16:00,650 --> 00:16:03,450
他知道真相后会怎么想？
What's he gonna think of me when he finds out?

301
00:16:04,490 --> 00:16:05,980
我也不知道
I don't know.

302
00:16:06,060 --> 00:16:08,320
不过如果你不告诉他
But if you don't tell him...

303
00:16:08,390 --> 00:16:10,730
就会失去这个儿子
...you're gonna lose him, Sammy.

304
00:16:35,620 --> 00:16:37,920
（勇猛骄傲，野性大发）

305
00:16:59,380 --> 00:17:01,610
绿色箱子
The green boxes.

306
00:17:04,350 --> 00:17:06,320
（野性大发）

307
00:17:40,150 --> 00:17:42,050
（禁区，请勿进入）

308
00:18:21,460 --> 00:18:23,520
全都装上去了
OK, they're all loaded up!

309
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:25,890
你以为我不知道吗？  走吧
You don't think I know that?  Get movin'!

310
00:18:25,970 --> 00:18:28,730
我改变主意了，我不想走
I changed my mind! I don't wanna go!

311
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:30,830
救命啊！
Help!

312
00:18:30,900 --> 00:18:32,500
雷恩
Ryan.

313
00:18:34,570 --> 00:18:36,060
救救我！
Help me!

314
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:37,670
小心！
Watch out!

315
00:18:38,610 --> 00:18:40,240
山大王！
Sam!

316
00:18:40,310 --> 00:18:42,180
等等我们  爸！
Wait for us!  Dad!

317
00:18:42,250 --> 00:18:44,150
雷恩！  爸！
Ryan!  Dad!

318
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:46,210
别让他们把我带走
Don't let them take me!

319
00:18:46,290 --> 00:18:48,720
不！  雷恩！
No!  Ryan!

320
00:18:48,790 --> 00:18:49,780
救命啊！
Help!

321
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:53,820
不！  爸，快来救我
No!  Dad! Help me!

322
00:18:53,890 --> 00:18:55,760
雷恩！
Ryan!

323
00:19:03,940 --> 00:19:06,910
斑尼，我们要追踪那辆卡车  收到
Benny, we need that truck followed.  Check.

324
00:19:06,970 --> 00:19:09,530
快去找…鸽子
Get me... the pigeons.

325
00:19:12,750 --> 00:19:15,080
我要一对六点
I am wanting snake eyes!

326
00:19:15,150 --> 00:19:17,050
来呀，宝贝
Come on, baby.

327
00:19:17,120 --> 00:19:18,740
快丢呀
Come on, just throw it.

328
00:19:24,820 --> 00:19:25,810
谢了
Thanks.

329
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:30,690
阿山，你是史上最大的输家
Hamir! You are the great loser of all time!

330
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:33,700
我到底该奉献什么给你呢？
What offerings must I make, I wonder?

331
00:19:33,770 --> 00:19:35,360
阿山！阿山！
Hamir! Hamir!

332
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:37,200
冷静一点
Get a grip on yourself!

333
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:42,710
斑尼，我要等到礼拜五 才能把钱还给你
Benny! I am needing till Friday before I am paying you back!

334
00:19:42,780 --> 00:19:44,240
不是啦，是雷恩
No, no. It's Ryan.

335
00:19:44,310 --> 00:19:47,280
他被装进绿色箱子 被他们带走了
He's in one of those green boxes and they took it away!

336
00:19:47,350 --> 00:19:48,780
我们一定要找到他
We've got to find him!

337
00:19:48,850 --> 00:19:51,650
事情大条了，情况不妙
That is not good! Not good at all!

338
00:19:53,120 --> 00:19:55,710
我知道啦
I know! I know!

339
00:19:55,790 --> 00:19:58,720
我正在告诉他 你们这些起肖的鸽子
I am telling him, you crazy pigeon!

340
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:02,920
绿色箱子会被带到大海
The green boxes go to the big water

341
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,520
海上有一个 头上有尖刺的女雕像
where stiff lady with spikes on her head...

342
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:08,430
阿山，我听不懂  尖刺呀！
Hamir? I can't understand...  Spikes!

343
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:12,160
告诉我绿色箱子去哪里
Just tell me where the green boxes go.

344
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:15,670
女雕像？尖刺？
Stiff lady, spikies?

345
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:18,500
没错，就像我太太说的
Yes, like my wife says,

346
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:22,450
卡车把他们载到她那里
the truck takes them to her! To her!

347
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:27,750
虽然我只喜欢报喜不报忧 不过我有更多坏消息
Though I hate telling bad news, there is more bad news to tell.

348
00:20:27,820 --> 00:20:31,920
天一亮，绿色箱子 就要搭船离开永远不会回来
When the sun rises, the green boxes leave on boat-boat and never return!

349
00:20:31,990 --> 00:20:35,120
（动物园到非洲拯救行动）

350
00:20:35,630 --> 00:20:38,830
真的很遗憾，我很难过
I am sorry for this. I really am.

351
00:20:40,500 --> 00:20:41,800
有人在吗？
Hello?

352
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:46,560
惨了，情况不妙
No. Not good. Not good.

353
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,440
你老是这么说
You always say that.

354
00:20:48,510 --> 00:20:50,910
我老是这么说，可是没人肯听
I keep on sayin' it. No one's listenin'.

355
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:52,910
就像一张跳针的老唱片
Like a broken record here.

356
00:20:52,980 --> 00:20:54,780
山大王，我们几时出发？
OK. When do we leave, Sammy?

357
00:20:54,850 --> 00:20:56,180
对啊，我们几时出发？
Yeah, when do we leave?

358
00:20:56,250 --> 00:20:59,840
不是我们，只有我 搞清楚
It's not "we." It's me. Let's make this clear.

359
00:20:59,920 --> 00:21:02,980
这是拯救行动 要去的只有我一个
This is now a rescue mission and I am the only one going.

360
00:21:03,060 --> 00:21:05,520
我们也要去，我们都不怕
We'll come too! We're not afraid.

361
00:21:05,590 --> 00:21:06,850
对吧，大伙儿？
Are we, guys?

362
00:21:06,930 --> 00:21:08,660
怕？当然不怕罗
Afraid? No.

363
00:21:08,730 --> 00:21:11,460
你们知道无尾熊嘛 我们只会发抖
You know koalas. More like "scared of things."

364
00:21:11,530 --> 00:21:13,230
雷恩就像咱们自己的小孩
Ryan's like a cub to all of us.

365
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:15,860
不过看来我这辈子 是不会有自己的小孩了
Not that I'll ever have one of my own at this rate.

366
00:21:15,940 --> 00:21:18,770
有一只有名的无尾熊说过
You know, there's that famous... A koala once said,

367
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:21,200
「我们要用…水蜜桃打他们」
"We will fight them... with peaches."

368
00:21:21,970 --> 00:21:23,670
是哦，言归正传
Yeah. Anyway.

369
00:21:23,740 --> 00:21:27,800
不管怎样，我们都要帮忙  你们要跟我来？好吧
So we're helping, whatever it takes.  You want to leave with me? OK.

370
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:31,340
如果你们不怕被猎捕、射杀
If you don't mind being hunted down, shot at...

371
00:21:31,420 --> 00:21:33,040
…被做成标本的话  好吧
...stuffed...  OK!

372
00:21:33,120 --> 00:21:35,140
或是更惨的事，那就来吧
...or worse, then fine.

373
00:21:35,220 --> 00:21:38,590
我经常做的恶梦就是 被剥皮和去斑
I have a recurring nightmare about taxidermy and spot remover.

374
00:21:38,660 --> 00:21:42,560
他们想抓到我门儿都没有 我跑得超快的
Well, they have to catch us before they can stuff us and I'm fast.

375
00:21:42,630 --> 00:21:45,720
除了我谁都不能去，了吗？
Nobody's leaving but me. Got it?

376
00:21:46,930 --> 00:21:48,370
你才是老大  没错
You're the boss.  You bet.

377
00:21:48,430 --> 00:21:50,200
你是万兽之王嘛  一点也没错
You got the big hair.  Absolutely.

378
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:51,900
好耶，好伎俩，山大王
Yeah, that's good, Sammy.

379
00:21:51,970 --> 00:21:54,440
先把最弱的成员踢掉
Hey, way to weed out the weak links.

380
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:57,340
他们不会碍事了 你有什么计划？
Now that they're out of the picture, what's the plan?

381
00:22:16,830 --> 00:22:19,320
（纽约市立动物园）

382
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:23,940
你放一百万个心，老大
Don't worry about a thing, big guy.

383
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,530
我早就想好了
I got it all taken care of.

384
00:22:25,610 --> 00:22:28,540
我对这城市
I know this city...

385
00:22:28,610 --> 00:22:30,100
…了若指掌
...like the back of my paw.

386
00:22:30,180 --> 00:22:33,580
咱们在第五大道下车 先左转两次，再右转两次
We ditch this truck at Fifth Avenue, couple lefts, couple rights,

387
00:22:33,650 --> 00:22:35,670
然后过了百老汇
bada-boom, past Broadway and...

388
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:40,210
…就到了
You're there!

389
00:22:45,990 --> 00:22:47,320
你跑来这儿干吗？
What are you doing here?

390
00:22:48,860 --> 00:22:52,090
什么？  我们是来帮你找到雷恩
What?  We're going to help you find Ryan!

391
00:22:52,160 --> 00:22:55,160
她说 「我们要帮你找到雷恩」
She said, "We're gonna help you find Ryan."

392
00:22:55,230 --> 00:22:57,000
太好了  喂，大伙儿
Oh, great.  Hey, guys.

393
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:58,870
我的屁眼塞了爆米花
I've got popcorn up my bum.

394
00:22:58,940 --> 00:22:59,930
（爆米花）
Do I look trashy in this?

395
00:23:00,010 --> 00:23:01,370
我穿这样会不会很俗？

396
00:23:02,210 --> 00:23:03,370
好吧，这是我的…
OK, here's my...

397
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:06,900
这是我的通盘计划 我们到底要去哪儿呀？
Here's my overall plan. Where are we going?

398
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:10,140
天亮之前如果不救出雷恩 他就永远不会回来
I only have until sunrise before Ryan is taken away forever!

399
00:23:10,220 --> 00:23:12,620
现在我还要担心你们三个？
And now I have to worry about you three?

400
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:16,990
好吧，斑尼，我们几时下车？
All right, fine. When do we get off of this thing, Benny?

401
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:18,390
斑尼也在这里？
Benny's here?

402
00:23:18,460 --> 00:23:20,450
是啊，他在那里
Yeah, he's right there.

403
00:23:21,530 --> 00:23:22,690
斑尼？
Benny?

404
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:24,720
斑尼！
Benny!

405
00:23:28,170 --> 00:23:30,330
这下好了，现在怎么办？
Great. Now what am I gonna do?

406
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:33,460
大伙儿，我们应该蹲下来
Guys! Guys! I think we should duck!

407
00:23:33,540 --> 00:23:34,670
她说什么？
What is she saying?

408
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:37,400
她说「蹲下来」
She said, "Duck down!"

409
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,810
蹲下来
Duck!

410
00:23:41,710 --> 00:23:43,980
我可没心情玩动手动脚
I am not in the mood for a game of footsie

411
00:23:44,050 --> 00:23:46,310
或是动蹄动掌的游戏
or hoofsie or pawsie or...

412
00:23:46,390 --> 00:23:48,550
那不是我的脚掌，是这玩意儿
That wasn't my paw. It was this!

413
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:52,960
我不是偷来的，是借来了
I didn't steal it. I borrowed it.

414
00:23:53,030 --> 00:23:56,020
可以照亮找到雷恩的路
It'll light the way to Ryan.

415
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:28,320
（玩具反斗城）

416
00:24:36,470 --> 00:24:39,060
（纽约市立动物园 生物研究中心）

417
00:25:00,090 --> 00:25:01,350
墙壁在动耶
The walls are moving.

418
00:25:01,430 --> 00:25:03,090
对哦，墙壁…
Right, right. The walls...

419
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:04,460
墙壁在动！
The walls are moving!

420
00:25:04,530 --> 00:25:06,560
赖瑞，憋住气
Larry, hold your breath!

421
00:25:09,770 --> 00:25:10,930
赖瑞，保持这样
Larry, stay straight!

422
00:25:12,970 --> 00:25:14,270
大家出去！
Everybody out!

423
00:25:14,340 --> 00:25:16,770
别紧张，我们只要…
All right, don't panic. What we've got to do...

424
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:25,250
情况很不妙，山大王！
This is definitely not good. Samson!

425
00:25:25,320 --> 00:25:28,220
把你的脚伸出来  救命啊！
Give me your hoof!  Help!

426
00:25:28,290 --> 00:25:29,580
赖瑞！
Larry!

427
00:25:33,530 --> 00:25:35,320
垃圾！它活过来了！
The garbage! It lives!

428
00:25:36,060 --> 00:25:38,150
（每平方寸）

429
00:25:40,870 --> 00:25:42,130
大伙儿？
Guys?

430
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:44,600
有人在吗？ 我吓呆了
OK, anybody? I'm freakin' out.

431
00:25:45,940 --> 00:25:48,270
你们在等什么？  有人吗？
What's the hold up?  Hello?

432
00:25:49,540 --> 00:25:51,100
我们在这里，尼啾
We're over here, Nigel.

433
00:25:51,180 --> 00:25:53,110
好，我马上来
Right. I'll be there in a minute.

434
00:25:53,180 --> 00:25:55,440
用力想，斑尼说什么？
Think. What did Benny say?

435
00:25:55,510 --> 00:25:58,750
先左转两次，再右转两次
Couple of lefts, couple of rights.

436
00:25:58,820 --> 00:26:00,650
BJ，你看得到绿色女士吗？
Bridget, can you see the green lady?

437
00:26:00,720 --> 00:26:02,690
我正在看，我正在看
I'm looking, I'm looking,

438
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:05,590
不过我什么也看不到
but I can't see over anything for a change.

439
00:26:05,660 --> 00:26:08,350
你们到底在哪里？ 另一个大陆吗？
How far are you away? You in a different continent?

440
00:26:08,430 --> 00:26:10,260
赖瑞，那是你吗？
Is that you, Larry?

441
00:26:10,330 --> 00:26:11,490
我在上面，尼啾
Up here, Nige.

442
00:26:12,570 --> 00:26:13,960
你这条蛇的毛还真多耶
You're a very furry snake.

443
00:26:14,030 --> 00:26:16,970
大伙儿，不要太引人注目
Guys... We don't want to draw attention to ourselves.

444
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:24,940
小狗狗，山大王 你一定觉得很好玩
Dogs. This should be fun for you, Samson.

445
00:26:25,010 --> 00:26:26,600
尼啾，抓住BJ！
Nigel! Grab Bridget!

446
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:28,870
什么？  快跑呀！
What?  Run!

447
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:34,350
我要吐了，我要吐了
I'm gonna throw up! I'm gonna throw up!

448
00:26:34,420 --> 00:26:37,150
你不是应该 把他们撕成碎片吗？
Shouldn't you be tearing them to shreds?

449
00:26:37,220 --> 00:26:41,460
这是计划的一部份 这一招叫赛伦盖提脱逃术
All part of the plan. This maneuver's known as the Serengeti Slip.

450
00:26:41,530 --> 00:26:44,050
「掠食动物教战手册」第十页
Page ten of the Predator's Playbook.

451
00:26:48,670 --> 00:26:49,660
现在怎么办？
What next?

452
00:26:51,270 --> 00:26:52,930
第十一页？
Page 11?

453
00:26:54,870 --> 00:26:56,470
尽管笑吧，杂种狗
Go on, you mutts!

454
00:26:56,540 --> 00:26:58,870
笨狗狗，我们大可以教训你们
Stupid dogs, we could've taken you.

455
00:27:01,450 --> 00:27:03,970
教你们…跳迪斯可
Taken you to a... To a disco!

456
00:27:05,220 --> 00:27:06,340
赖瑞，想想办法
Larry, improvise!

457
00:27:08,420 --> 00:27:10,680
赖瑞，你愈帮愈忙  好吧
Larry, that's not helping.  OK.

458
00:27:10,760 --> 00:27:14,060
你们这些逊狗以为很会狗叫？ 山大王可是会狮子吼耶
You dogs think you got bark? Well, Samson's got roar!

459
00:27:14,130 --> 00:27:16,290
让他们瞧瞧你的厉害  秀出你的本领
Show 'em, Sam.  Dig deep, Samson.

460
00:27:16,360 --> 00:27:18,890
你是一头狮子，大显神威吧
You're a lion. Be a lion.

461
00:27:20,970 --> 00:27:22,960
看看那家伙
Look at that guy!

462
00:27:24,770 --> 00:27:26,930
山大王，他们口吐白沫
Sam, they are frothing at the mouth.

463
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:30,330
好吧
OK...

464
00:27:30,410 --> 00:27:32,140
赖瑞，卷起来  收到
Larry, coil!  Check!

465
00:27:38,520 --> 00:27:41,510
山大王  这是随机应变，快跳啊
Sam!  I improvised. Now jump!

466
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:42,920
跳下去？  对
Down there?  Yes!

467
00:27:47,030 --> 00:27:48,990
我们要走了哦，赖瑞
We're leaving, Larry!

468
00:28:06,410 --> 00:28:09,900
山大王，我只想问你哦 你碰到刚才那些狗
Teensy question, Samson. With those dogs up there,

469
00:28:09,980 --> 00:28:12,970
为什么不像你在 大草原那样对付他们？
why didn't you just do what you did in the wild?

470
00:28:13,050 --> 00:28:15,040
你知道嘛 冲上去把他们扑倒
You know, lionize 'em or lionate them

471
00:28:15,120 --> 00:28:16,710
把他们吓得皮皮挫？
or lionify them?

472
00:28:16,790 --> 00:28:19,160
我没时间和小狗穷磨菇
I don't have time to fight dogs, Bridget.

473
00:28:19,220 --> 00:28:21,420
我们得找到雷恩，记得吗？
We have to find Ryan, remember?

474
00:28:21,490 --> 00:28:23,590
这是什么鬼地方？
What is this stinky place?

475
00:28:23,660 --> 00:28:25,820
这地方
Lt...

476
00:28:25,900 --> 00:28:27,960
…看起来是人类洗澡的地方
...appears to be a human bathing area.

477
00:28:28,030 --> 00:28:30,970
你是说人类 不是把自己舔干净？
You mean humans don't lick themselves clean?

478
00:28:31,040 --> 00:28:32,500
真恶心
Disgusting!

479
00:28:32,570 --> 00:28:36,440
他们真是无药可救 很难想像他们在统治世界
They're hopeless. It is hard to believe they are at the top of the food chain.

480
00:28:36,510 --> 00:28:40,270
我无法想像 他们从不把自己舔干净
I can't imagine beginning the day without licking myself.

481
00:28:40,350 --> 00:28:42,840
我不是在催你哦 不过你有计划吗？
No hurry, but is there a plan?

482
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:45,320
当然有罗
Of course there's a plan.

483
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:47,780
我们沿着这条水道到大海
We follow this water to the big water,

484
00:28:47,850 --> 00:28:49,910
然后找到那个…
and then we find the lady with...

485
00:28:53,560 --> 00:28:57,590
赖瑞，如果不是你肚子在叫 就是你肚子里有东西在叫
Larry, either your stomach is growling or something in it is growling.

486
00:28:57,660 --> 00:28:59,320
又不是我
Wasn't me.

487
00:29:01,470 --> 00:29:03,060
干吗？
What?

488
00:29:08,740 --> 00:29:12,840
干得好，尼啾  哇塞，双胞胎耶
Smooth move, Nigel!  Oh, boy! Twins!

489
00:29:12,910 --> 00:29:15,380
山大王，快一点 这两个家伙
OK, Sammy, hurry it up now, 'cause these guys

490
00:29:15,450 --> 00:29:17,920
…好像肚子很饿
are seeming to have acid reflux or something!

491
00:29:17,980 --> 00:29:20,540
大伙儿冷静点
Everybody... stay calm.

492
00:29:20,620 --> 00:29:22,180
冷静？  不好了
Calm?  Not good.

493
00:29:26,390 --> 00:29:28,160
喂，吓你们的啦
Yo. Boo!

494
00:29:29,760 --> 00:29:32,490
你和你的麻吉们好像
I'm gonna say, it looks like you and your crew here

495
00:29:32,560 --> 00:29:34,430
…离你们的家园太远了吧
are a little far from your borough.

496
00:29:36,570 --> 00:29:38,300
离你们的家园太远了  好好笑哦
Far from your borough! I love it.

497
00:29:38,370 --> 00:29:40,030
我们要去大海那边
We're going to the big water.

498
00:29:40,110 --> 00:29:42,510
尼啾，比一比我们要找什么
Nigel, show them what we're looking for.

499
00:29:44,310 --> 00:29:46,640
像这样吗？  她是用右手拿
Like this?  I think it's in her right hand.

500
00:29:50,320 --> 00:29:53,220
她不是蓝色的吗？  我不会变色
And isn't she blue?  I can't do blue.

501
00:29:53,290 --> 00:29:56,080
你不知道吧？  完全没印象
No idea. You?  Doesn't even register.

502
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:58,750
你比得超逊的  不然就比…
You're battin' zero, kid.  Do the thing with...

503
00:29:59,530 --> 00:30:01,820
拜托你快点决定
Make your bloody mind up.

504
00:30:02,800 --> 00:30:05,700
头上有尖刺的那个女巨人
The big female with the spikes on her melon!

505
00:30:05,760 --> 00:30:07,100
他们是观光客
They're tourists.

506
00:30:07,170 --> 00:30:10,730
观光客，听好了 你们得去炮台公园
All right, tourists, listen up. Ya gotta get to Battery Park.

507
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:12,670
先钻进百老汇的排水沟
First take the Broadway culvert.

508
00:30:12,740 --> 00:30:15,940
钻进百老汇的排水沟？  那有什么问题？
Down the Broadway culvert?  What's wrong with that?

509
00:30:16,010 --> 00:30:18,670
他们会在废水处理厂迷路  少来了
They get lost at the sewage plant!  Get outta here!

510
00:30:18,740 --> 00:30:21,210
你在说什么呀？  要不然要怎么走？
What are you talking about?  How would you send 'em?

511
00:30:21,280 --> 00:30:22,840
你指的路不对啦
You're sendin' 'em the wrong way!

512
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:25,750
华尔街在修路 排水沟被堵住了
The Wall Street culvert is blocked with construction.

513
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:27,380
那也对  好吧
That is true.  All right.

514
00:30:27,450 --> 00:30:29,010
两位，你们到底帮不帮忙？
Guys, you gonna help or not?

515
00:30:29,090 --> 00:30:31,820
当然帮忙罗 我们一定会帮到底
Yeah, sure. Of course we're gonna help ya's.

516
00:30:31,890 --> 00:30:34,090
咱们都是一家人，对吧？
We're one big family, right?

517
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:36,420
除了那个家伙 他把我给吓…
Except for that guy there. He scares the...

518
00:30:36,500 --> 00:30:40,060
你有完没完呀，卡麦？
You done runnin' your mouth yet, Carmine? Are ya?

519
00:30:40,130 --> 00:30:43,860
抱歉，他曾经被冲下马桶 到现在还余悸犹存
I apologize. He never got over being flushed down the toilet.

520
00:30:44,900 --> 00:30:45,890
是啊
Yeah.

521
00:30:45,970 --> 00:30:49,630
跟我来，你们在这里 肯定活不了十分钟
Follow me, 'cause you four won't last ten minutes in this neighborhood.

522
00:30:49,710 --> 00:30:51,140
这地方是大草原
It's a jungle down here.

523
00:30:51,210 --> 00:30:53,510
史旦，你知道他是谁吗？  什么？不知道
Stan, you know who that is?  What? No.

524
00:30:53,580 --> 00:30:55,980
他是会说话的无尾熊
That's one of them talkin' kawana bears!

525
00:30:56,050 --> 00:30:58,710
你好吗？
How ya doing?

526
00:30:58,780 --> 00:31:00,980
我超可爱的，我喜欢你
I'm so cuddly! I like you!

527
00:31:03,190 --> 00:31:06,280
我看过一大堆无尾熊玩偶 从下水道流下来
I've seen a lot of those things floatin' here in the sewer.

528
00:31:07,530 --> 00:31:10,260
超好笑的 你害我笑到不行
That's good! You're makin' me laugh over here.

529
00:31:10,330 --> 00:31:12,020
等等我
Just wait for me!

530
00:31:21,210 --> 00:31:22,940
我们来对地方了吗？
Are we in the right place?

531
00:31:23,010 --> 00:31:25,410
只要没有那两只搞笑的鳄鱼
Any place without two hilarious alligators

532
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:27,410
应该就对了
seems a move in the right direction.

533
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:32,350
山大王，你看到什么吗？  看到了
Sam, do you see anything up there?  I sure do.

534
00:31:33,750 --> 00:31:36,880
她就在那里 就跟阿山说的一样
Well, well, well. There she is, like Hamir said.

535
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:40,980
天亮了 咱们的时间不多了
And it's sunrise, which means we're a tad short on time.

536
00:31:41,060 --> 00:31:43,430
大伙儿，听好 雷恩被关在绿色箱子
Guys, look. We know the box Ryan's in is green.

537
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:46,120
一定就在这附近 我要你们…
It's gotta be around here, so I need you to...

538
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:48,530
知道啦，看到箱子就大叫
Yeah. So we should shout out if we see a box

539
00:31:48,600 --> 00:31:50,760
就像那边的那些箱子
that looks like the ones over there.

540
00:31:52,040 --> 00:31:54,160
还没运走，我们追得回来
It hasn't left yet! We can make it!

541
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:56,140
快走吧  抓紧了，赖瑞
Let's go!  Hold on, Larry!

542
00:32:00,450 --> 00:32:03,010
往哪儿走？  对啊，哪儿？
Which way now?  Yeah, which way?

543
00:32:04,120 --> 00:32:06,450
快跑！
Run!

544
00:32:12,090 --> 00:32:13,680
不！
No!

545
00:32:13,760 --> 00:32:15,350
不！
No!

546
00:32:15,430 --> 00:32:17,020
雷恩在那上面
Ryan's on that thing!

547
00:32:17,100 --> 00:32:18,650
我们一定要阻止它
We've got to stop it!

548
00:32:18,730 --> 00:32:20,860
不行啦，山大王  我不管
We can't, Sam!  I don't care!

549
00:32:20,930 --> 00:32:23,420
不行啦，你会淹死的 山大王！
No, Sammy, you'll drown!  Sam!

550
00:32:30,340 --> 00:32:33,070
我又失败了
I failed. Again.

551
00:32:33,150 --> 00:32:35,270
我只失败过这么一次
I only count one failure.

552
00:32:35,350 --> 00:32:37,980
彻底的大失败 不过就这么一次
It's big, but it's just one.

553
00:32:38,050 --> 00:32:42,080
再见了，雷恩 我们会很想念你
Goodbye, Ryan. We're gonna miss ya.

554
00:32:44,820 --> 00:32:47,920
山大王！  这到底是怎么回事？
Samson!  What on earth is going on?

555
00:32:47,990 --> 00:32:52,090
那是个人类 他不是替动物园工作
It's a human and I do not think he works for the zoo.

556
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:54,720
也许现在应该要随机应变
Perhaps now is a good time to improvise.

557
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:56,130
什么？
What?

558
00:33:02,710 --> 00:33:05,640
太好了，解决了一个问题
Great! One problem down...

559
00:33:05,740 --> 00:33:07,180
棒呆了
Far out.

560
00:33:07,250 --> 00:33:08,770
酷哦
Cool.

561
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:11,710
又遇上一个大灾难
One disaster to go.

562
00:33:19,860 --> 00:33:22,620
你在干什么？ 我们要撞上另一艘船了
What are you doing? We're headed for the other boat!

563
00:33:22,690 --> 00:33:24,860
这要怎么开呀？ 谁知道要怎么开船？
How do we steer? Who knows how to steer?

564
00:33:24,930 --> 00:33:27,630
谁都不会 我们只是动物，这下可好了
None of us. We're animals. Great!

565
00:33:39,980 --> 00:33:42,570
等等，赖瑞，再做一次  做什么？
Hold on, Larry. Do that again.  Do what?

566
00:33:42,650 --> 00:33:44,780
你刚才那样 不过这次要反方向
Whatever you just did, but the opposite!

567
00:33:44,850 --> 00:33:47,440
我不知道反方向是哪里
But I don't know my opposites!

568
00:33:48,350 --> 00:33:49,880
不对，像这样
No, Larry, like this!

569
00:33:58,900 --> 00:34:00,870
我好像学会了
I think I've got it.

570
00:34:03,340 --> 00:34:05,130
很简单嘛
Well, that was easy.

571
00:34:06,100 --> 00:34:09,400
天啊，谁有尤加利叶？ 我要擦屁屁
Oh, dear. Has anyone got any eucalyptus wipes?

572
00:34:09,470 --> 00:34:11,640
这并不难嘛
This isn't so difficult.

573
00:34:11,710 --> 00:34:14,700
我是大海的狮王
I'm the lion of the sea!

574
00:34:15,810 --> 00:34:17,300
干得好
Well done, sir.

575
00:34:17,380 --> 00:34:20,580
你是咱们的队长 现在是这艘船的船长
Captain of our team and now captain of this vessel.

576
00:34:20,650 --> 00:34:21,680
你超棒的
You're brilliant.

577
00:34:21,750 --> 00:34:26,520
我不想扫兴 不过在一片混乱中
I hate to be Miss Negative, but in this melee,

578
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:28,530
我们把雷恩的船追丢了
we seem to have lost Ryan's boat.

579
00:34:28,590 --> 00:34:32,720
什么？啥都没有？  对，它不见了
What, nothing?  Nothing. He's gone.

580
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,730
不
No.

581
00:34:44,740 --> 00:34:47,270
那里，尼森，绿色箱子
There! Nelson! The green boxes!

582
00:34:47,350 --> 00:34:49,640
你确定？  我的麻吉在那里
You're sure, eh?  And there's my buddies!

583
00:34:49,720 --> 00:34:51,810
还有我的最爱
And my love!

584
00:34:51,880 --> 00:34:55,280
我们下去吧
Let's go in!

585
00:34:56,490 --> 00:34:59,950
我们要背着太阳走  不，要朝着太阳往北走
We'll head away from the sun.  No, towards the sun. To the north.

586
00:35:00,030 --> 00:35:02,080
右舷…左舷
Starboard... Leftboard.

587
00:35:02,160 --> 00:35:03,820
跟着我的指头就对了
Just follow my finger.

588
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:06,090
拜托，就算答案从天而降
Please. You guys wouldn't know the answer

589
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:08,560
打到你们头上 你们也不会知道
if it fell from the sky and hit you in the head.

590
00:35:08,630 --> 00:35:10,620
天啊，有一只蝙蝠
Oh, my! It's a bat! It's a bat!

591
00:35:10,700 --> 00:35:12,690
快把他弄掉，快弄掉
Get it off me! Get it off me!

592
00:35:14,870 --> 00:35:16,810
斑尼！  斑尼？
Benny!  Benny?

593
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,100
天鹅！
Geese!

594
00:35:19,610 --> 00:35:23,050
你没事吧？  没事，我的公主
Are you all right?  Yes, my princess.

595
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,810
斑尼，你来了
Benny, you made it!

596
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:30,750
你们是我的好朋友 好朋友应该团结一致
You're my best friend. Best friends should stick together.

597
00:35:30,820 --> 00:35:32,760
就算不怎么好的朋友也要
Even not-so-best friends,

598
00:35:32,820 --> 00:35:35,260
竟然把我 从急驶的垃圾车上踢下去
who knock you off a speeding garbage truck.

599
00:35:35,330 --> 00:35:38,490
对不起啦 不过我求他们回去找你
Excuse me, but I begged them to go back and get you.

600
00:35:38,560 --> 00:35:39,550
这一点我要说清楚哦
Just so you know.

601
00:35:39,630 --> 00:35:42,600
斑尼，你在上面 看得到雷恩的船吗？
Benny, could you see Ryan's boat from up there?

602
00:35:42,670 --> 00:35:45,730
我正好看到它往那里走
Well, it just so happens I saw it heading that way.

603
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:47,270
而且我们很幸运
And we're in luck!

604
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:50,270
你们好吗？  加拿大野雁
How's it goin', eh?  Canadian geese!

605
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:53,210
勇闯天涯旅行专家
Experts at intercontinental travel.

606
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,940
嗨，小鸟，我问你哦
Hey, birdie, OK,

607
00:35:55,010 --> 00:35:59,850
加拿大的移民政策 是不是对无尾熊特别宽待？
is it true that Canada has lax immigration policies for koalas?

608
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:02,320
我问就好 我儿子被带走了
I'll take it from here. My son's out there.

609
00:36:02,390 --> 00:36:05,620
我们真的需要你们帮忙 你们能带我们找到那艘船吗？
We really need your help. Can you lead us to that boat?

610
00:36:05,690 --> 00:36:08,630
没问题，跟着我们就行了
No problem, eh? Just follow us and Bob's your uncle.

611
00:36:08,690 --> 00:36:11,820
不要落后太远，好吗？
Try not to lag too far behind, eh?

612
00:36:13,500 --> 00:36:15,990
斑尼，谢了
Hey, Benny, thanks.

613
00:36:16,070 --> 00:36:21,940
对了，你掉下去的时候 BJ很担心你哦
And FYI, Bridget was very concerned when you fell off the truck.

614
00:36:26,180 --> 00:36:29,980
我打赌你一定不知道 我会骑野雁，对吧？
Bet you didn't know I could ride geese, did you?

615
00:36:30,050 --> 00:36:32,410
厉害吧？  拜托
Bareback.  Oh, brother.

616
00:36:35,390 --> 00:36:38,580
山大王？ 我们要去大草原吗？
Sammy? We going to the wild now?

617
00:36:38,660 --> 00:36:41,320
应该是吧，赖瑞
I think we are, Larry.

618
00:36:53,240 --> 00:36:57,040
（纽约大西洋）

619
00:37:42,520 --> 00:37:44,850
我受不了了
I can't take it anymore.

620
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:46,860
他在耍我们，你们听
He's taunting us! Listen!

621
00:37:48,930 --> 00:37:51,860
别再笑我们了，臭太阳
Stop laughing at us, you solar twit!

622
00:37:51,930 --> 00:37:55,530
山大王船长 有没有冰淇淋吃？
Captain Bligh, sir! Are the ice cream cones ready?

623
00:37:55,600 --> 00:37:57,900
船员就快要发动叛变了
The crew, they're on the verge of mutiny.

624
00:37:57,970 --> 00:37:59,060
尼啾，拜托
Nigel, please.

625
00:37:59,140 --> 00:38:01,660
不给我们吃冰淇淋
If you don't give us ice creams pretty quick,

626
00:38:01,740 --> 00:38:03,470
我们就要逼你跳进大海
you're gonna walk the plank, sir!

627
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:05,530
尼啾  我不管我会不会淹死
Nigel.  I don't care if I drown,

628
00:38:05,610 --> 00:38:08,200
我只想马上离开这艘幽灵船
I'm getting off this death cruise right now.

629
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:15,150
冰山！ 我要和这艘船共生死
Iceberg! Permission to go down with the ship, sir.

630
00:38:15,220 --> 00:38:16,980
等一下，这话我收回
Hang on! Stuff that!

631
00:38:17,060 --> 00:38:20,320
快跑啊！游泳！
Run! Swim!

632
00:38:20,390 --> 00:38:21,520
尼啾？
Nigel?

633
00:38:21,590 --> 00:38:24,890
瞧，我是海星耶
Look, I'm a starfish.

634
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:27,090
大伙儿，你们看
Guys, look.

635
00:38:27,170 --> 00:38:30,620
天啊，你一定觉得 花了一辈子才到
Gosh. Must feel like a lifetime since you've been here.

636
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:33,640
是啊，一辈子
Yeah... a lifetime.

637
00:38:45,380 --> 00:38:46,710
搞什么鬼？
What the heck?

638
00:38:46,790 --> 00:38:49,020
哇，你们看
Wow! Look!

639
00:38:49,090 --> 00:38:52,490
他们把绿色箱子放回大草原
They're releasing the green boxes back into the wild.

640
00:38:52,560 --> 00:38:53,750
赖瑞  大伙儿
Larry.  Guys,

641
00:38:53,830 --> 00:38:56,350
他们把动物又装进绿色箱子
they're putting animals inside the green boxes.

642
00:38:56,430 --> 00:38:58,560
我搞不懂为什么
I just can't figure out why.

643
00:38:58,630 --> 00:39:01,660
那是通往另一个空间的通道
It's a tunnel to another dimension, can't you see?

644
00:39:01,730 --> 00:39:03,530
他们先进去…  这家伙是谁？
They go in...  Who is this guy?

645
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:04,860
没关系，尼啾
It's all right, Nigel.

646
00:39:04,940 --> 00:39:07,340
你想这跟那玩意有关吗？
Think it has anything to do with that?

647
00:39:08,340 --> 00:39:12,210
等一下，如果我不是饿昏了头 就是赖瑞说的有道理
Hang on a second. Either I'm starving or Larry is making sense.

648
00:39:12,280 --> 00:39:15,680
你说得对 有人在拯救那些动物
You're right. Those animals are being rescued.

649
00:39:31,130 --> 00:39:32,460
雷恩？
Ryan?

650
00:39:33,900 --> 00:39:35,230
雷恩！
Ryan!

651
00:39:38,370 --> 00:39:39,600
噢，不！
Oh, no!

652
00:39:40,610 --> 00:39:41,590
雷恩！
Ryan!

653
00:39:45,010 --> 00:39:46,670
我们要快一点
We've got to move fast!

654
00:39:46,750 --> 00:39:48,470
雷恩！
Ryan!

655
00:39:51,780 --> 00:39:54,180
雷恩！雷恩！
Ryan! Ryan!

656
00:39:56,860 --> 00:39:59,520
雷恩！ 儿子，你在哪里？
Ryan! Where are you, buddy?

657
00:40:01,860 --> 00:40:03,450
雷恩！
Ryan!

658
00:40:03,530 --> 00:40:05,220
我不敢相信  山大王
I can't believe it!  Samson!

659
00:40:05,300 --> 00:40:07,590
我离他这么近，他就在那里
I was so close. He was right there!

660
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:09,830
现在找不到他了  过来
We'll never find him now!  Come here!

661
00:40:09,900 --> 00:40:14,170
冷静一点，用你的直觉
Will you get a hold of yourself? Use your instincts.

662
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:15,730
我不想再跑了
I don't want to run anymore.

663
00:40:15,810 --> 00:40:18,370
那敢情好，老实说 你需要好一点的运动内衣
Good. 'Cause frankly, you need a good sports bra.

664
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:20,410
雷恩？  一切都能搞定
Ryan?  Everything's under control.

665
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:23,380
失败只是暂时的  我闻到了
Temporary setback.  I got it.

666
00:40:23,450 --> 00:40:25,380
我闻到雷恩的味道  他闻到了？
I got Ryan's scent!  He got it?

667
00:40:25,450 --> 00:40:26,880
他闻到了耶！快走吧！
I mean, he got it! Let's go!

668
00:40:26,950 --> 00:40:29,280
万岁！  等等我们！
Hooray!  Wait for us!

669
00:40:29,890 --> 00:40:32,550
我不是赛跑选手 我需要一辆车
I'm not designed for this! I want a car.

670
00:40:35,290 --> 00:40:38,160
大伙儿，我找到他了 雷恩！
Hey, guys, I found him! Ryan!

671
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,630
你们不敲门的吗？
Doesn't anyone knock anymore?

672
00:40:41,700 --> 00:40:43,960
我儿子呢？ 他有没有来过这里？
Where's my son? Did he come through here?

673
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:48,030
对哦，我想起来了 他是来过这里，哈罗
Yeah, now that I think about it, he did come through here. Hello?

674
00:40:48,110 --> 00:40:51,010
出来吧，小狮子 你老爸来了
Come on out, baby lion! Your dad's here!

675
00:40:51,080 --> 00:40:54,340
有没有看到 这儿有一大堆狮子
Well, what do you know? There's a whole pride of lions here!

676
00:40:56,950 --> 00:41:00,180
臭死了 我以为你闻到雷恩的味道
Funky. I was under the impression you had Ryan's scent,

677
00:41:00,250 --> 00:41:02,740
不是这个臭得要命的家伙
not this olfactory insult.

678
00:41:02,820 --> 00:41:03,980
我…
I...

679
00:41:04,060 --> 00:41:07,960
我本来闻到雷恩的味道 不过我的掠食动物本能发作
I had Ryan's scent, but my predator instincts must've kicked in since,

680
00:41:08,030 --> 00:41:10,020
因为我有好久没吃东西了
you know, I haven't eaten for a while.

681
00:41:10,100 --> 00:41:11,530
一点也没错
Exactly!

682
00:41:11,600 --> 00:41:14,390
你永远不知道 掠食动物的本能几时发作
You never know when those instincts are gonna kick in.

683
00:41:14,470 --> 00:41:16,060
太好了，棒呆了
Excellent. Fantastic!

684
00:41:16,130 --> 00:41:18,000
我们终于要看到 传奇的山大王发威
We get to see the legend in action.

685
00:41:18,070 --> 00:41:20,130
我也很想呀，不过没时间了
I'd love to, but we just don't have time.

686
00:41:20,210 --> 00:41:23,470
当然有时间，山大王
We got the time, Sammy. Just...

687
00:41:23,540 --> 00:41:25,810
你先这样，然后再这样
And then you do this. And then this bit.

688
00:41:26,710 --> 00:41:28,700
一口把他撕裂
