蛮牛！ 蛮牛，别听他的
Kazar!  Kazar! Don't listen to him!

866
00:52:29,170 --> 00:52:31,600
蛮牛，听我说  蛮牛，这里
Kazar! Over here!  Kazar! Over here!

867
00:52:31,670 --> 00:52:34,840
你胆敢打断我拜见神兽
How dare you interrupt my audience with the Great Him!

868
00:52:34,910 --> 00:52:38,280
可是…我们找到一只小狮子
But... but we found a lion cub!

869
00:52:39,680 --> 00:52:41,610
真的假的？  他旁边有一只大狮子吗？
You did?  Was he with a big lion?

870
00:52:41,680 --> 00:52:44,150
有长长的鬃毛？ 其实只是后面很长啦
With big hair? Well, a mullet, really.

871
00:52:44,220 --> 00:52:47,710
伟大的神兽 你带来两头狮子？
Oh, Great Him, you brought two lions with you?

872
00:52:47,790 --> 00:52:50,050
我就像其它神兽一样
Well, like any Great Him,

873
00:52:50,120 --> 00:52:52,560
出门旅行都会带保镳
I travel with an entourage.

874
00:52:53,290 --> 00:52:57,060
放心，伟大的神兽 我会叫布雷把狮子带来
Worry not, Your Himness, I shall have Blag bring the lions here.

875
00:52:57,130 --> 00:53:01,690
这次他最好别搞砸 别像刚刚那样搞砸我的编舞
And he better not screw this up, like you screwed up my dance number!

876
00:53:01,770 --> 00:53:03,900
我只落后了一小音节
I lost count for one verse.

877
00:53:03,970 --> 00:53:06,340
向前踢，向侧踢、向前走
Step-kick, pivot-kick, walk, walk, walk.

878
00:53:07,280 --> 00:53:10,970
我们干吗那么辛苦练舞？
Why do we even bother rehearsing?

879
00:53:12,150 --> 00:53:14,670
好的舞群真的很难找耶
A good chorus line is so hard to put together.

880
00:53:17,420 --> 00:53:18,820
快飞上天呀
Take to the skies!

881
00:53:18,890 --> 00:53:20,820
我们这就飞了
We're taking! We're taking!

882
00:53:22,960 --> 00:53:25,550
快去找到他们  遵命，老大
Find them!  Yes, sir.

883
00:53:25,630 --> 00:53:28,360
把狮子给我带来
Bring us those lions!

884
00:53:31,830 --> 00:53:36,200
众神在庆祝预言终于实现
The gods celebrate the fulfillment of the prophecy.

885
00:53:36,270 --> 00:53:38,860
我们一起用力踏步
We stamp our hooves

886
00:53:38,940 --> 00:53:41,770
赞颂伟大的神兽
in praise of the Great Him!

887
00:53:41,840 --> 00:53:43,670
我的妈啊
Holy moly!

888
00:53:43,740 --> 00:53:45,940
我的妈啊  我的妈啊
Holy moly Holy moly

889
00:53:46,010 --> 00:53:49,210
你是万兽之王
You are our king!

890
00:54:05,130 --> 00:54:08,430
你看，那是谁？
Looky, looky who's there.

891
00:54:09,500 --> 00:54:10,770
惊喜！
Surprise!

892
00:54:13,370 --> 00:54:14,740
不！
No!

893
00:54:16,780 --> 00:54:18,750
抱歉我们来晚了
Sorry we're late for dinner!

894
00:54:27,760 --> 00:54:29,150
逊毙了
That's pathetic!

895
00:54:31,630 --> 00:54:32,790
滚开
Get off!

896
00:54:32,860 --> 00:54:34,830
一点都不痛  住手
That didn't hurt!  Stop!

897
00:54:38,130 --> 00:54:40,330
雷恩！  不！
Ryan!  No!

898
00:54:41,670 --> 00:54:43,400
我来了，儿子
I'm coming, son!

899
00:54:45,040 --> 00:54:46,730
爸？
Dad?

900
00:54:46,810 --> 00:54:48,670
救命啊  咱们快闪吧
Help!  Let's scram!

901
00:54:48,740 --> 00:54:50,640
雷恩！  你怎么会在这里？
Ryan!  What are you doing here?

902
00:54:50,710 --> 00:54:53,340
我不敢相信，我找到你了  你是怎么找到我的？
I can't believe it! I found you.  How'd you find me?

903
00:54:53,410 --> 00:54:55,440
你没事吧？有没有受伤？
Are you all right? Are you hurt?

904
00:54:55,520 --> 00:54:57,450
你的脚掌  我被困在绿色箱子
Your paw.  I got trapped in that box.

905
00:54:57,520 --> 00:54:58,850
没事了，儿子
It's OK, son.

906
00:54:58,920 --> 00:55:01,550
后来我逃出来，逃进丛林
And then I escaped, and I ran into the jungle...

907
00:55:01,620 --> 00:55:04,320
然后这些兀鹰飞来想杀死我
...then those vultures came and tried to kill me.

908
00:55:04,390 --> 00:55:07,020
你一定不怕他们 不过我好怕哦
You wouldn't have been scared. I was.

909
00:55:07,090 --> 00:55:09,460
我有件事要告诉你  什么事？
I have to tell you something.  What?

910
00:55:10,030 --> 00:55:11,500
你听
Listen.

911
00:55:13,000 --> 00:55:14,590
爸，去搞定他们  快跑啊！
Get 'em, Dad!  Run!

912
00:55:15,240 --> 00:55:16,860
快跑！
Run!

913
00:55:17,540 --> 00:55:20,030
爸，你应该追他们
Dad, you should be chasing them!

914
00:55:20,110 --> 00:55:22,510
就像你以前一样  那些只是我说的故事
Like you used to!  Those were just stories!

915
00:55:22,580 --> 00:55:24,910
现在你有机会证明那是真的
But now's your chance to show me for real!

916
00:55:28,680 --> 00:55:30,450
这边
This way!

917
00:55:33,850 --> 00:55:38,420
爸，怎么回事？  先爬到树上再说
Dad? What's goin' on?  Just get up into that tree!

918
00:55:44,930 --> 00:55:47,090
我们甩掉他们了  怎么回事？
I think we lost them.  What's the deal?

919
00:55:47,170 --> 00:55:49,190
他们只是一群逊脚
They're just a bunch of wimpy donkeys!

920
00:55:49,270 --> 00:55:50,900
你大可以把他们打得落花流水
You could kick their rumps!

921
00:55:50,970 --> 00:55:54,530
雷恩，我打不过他们  胆小鬼，给我回来
Ryan, I can't fight them.  You donkey-chickens! Get back here!

922
00:55:54,610 --> 00:55:56,700
雷恩，我打不过他们
Ryan! I can't fight them.

923
00:55:57,610 --> 00:55:59,370
什么意思？
What do you mean?

924
00:56:01,450 --> 00:56:03,540
我小时候
I was young...

925
00:56:03,620 --> 00:56:05,740
还只是只小狮子
...still just a cub.

926
00:56:06,690 --> 00:56:08,950
各位先生女士
Ladies and gentlemen.

927
00:56:09,020 --> 00:56:11,180
可爱的小朋友
Children of all ages.

928
00:56:11,260 --> 00:56:14,590
山大王 别害怕，抬头挺胸
Samson! Swallow that fear and stand tall!

929
00:56:14,660 --> 00:56:18,600
目睹这只小狮子 一生中最重要的一天
Witness the greatest day in our young lion's life!

930
00:56:18,670 --> 00:56:22,570
他张嘴大吼的一天
The day he discovers his roar!

931
00:56:22,640 --> 00:56:24,330
爸，我办不到
Dad, I can't do it!

932
00:56:24,410 --> 00:56:25,900
快去吧
Now, go!

933
00:56:25,970 --> 00:56:29,880
听小山大王发出 震耳欲聋的吼声
Listen as Samson unleashes a roar so mighty,

934
00:56:29,940 --> 00:56:33,400
把一头牛羚震出大草原
it launches a wildebeest clear off the savannah!

935
00:56:37,920 --> 00:56:40,390
小山大王，鼓起勇气
Samson! Dig deep!

936
00:56:52,630 --> 00:56:54,120
我早就知道
I should have known.

937
00:56:54,200 --> 00:56:58,260
如果你生在大草原 就会知道怎么发出吼声
If you'd been born in the wild, you'd know how to roar.

938
00:56:58,610 --> 00:56:59,660
爸？
Dad?

939
00:57:00,810 --> 00:57:03,400
爸！爸！
Dad! Dad!

940
00:57:03,480 --> 00:57:05,410
求求你
Please!

941
00:57:08,220 --> 00:57:09,680
爸
Dad.

942
00:57:09,750 --> 00:57:12,810
当他们把我送到动物园 我不想让任何人知道
When they shipped me to the zoo, I never wanted anyone to know

943
00:57:12,890 --> 00:57:17,120
…我来自哪里 尤其是我最亲近的朋友
where I came from. Especially those closest to me.

944
00:57:17,190 --> 00:57:19,280
我应该早一点告诉你
I should have told you sooner.

945
00:57:19,360 --> 00:57:22,800
可是…你说的那些故事？
But... all those stories you tell?

946
00:57:22,860 --> 00:57:25,760
对不起，雷恩
I'm so sorry, Ryan.

947
00:57:25,830 --> 00:57:28,860
你跟我说的一切都是谎言？
Everything you told me was a lie?

948
00:57:31,010 --> 00:57:33,410
爸！  抓紧了，儿子
Dad!  Hang on, son.

949
00:57:34,340 --> 00:57:36,310
救命啊！
Help!

950
00:57:36,410 --> 00:57:38,340
雷恩！
Ryan!

951
00:57:39,980 --> 00:57:42,110
雷恩！快跑！
Ryan! Run!

952
00:57:44,490 --> 00:57:46,510
想都别想，小鬼
Not so fast, Tigger.

953
00:57:48,190 --> 00:57:49,920
爸！
Dad!

954
00:57:51,790 --> 00:57:53,760
雷恩！
Ryan!

955
00:57:53,830 --> 00:57:55,260
爸！
Dad!

956
00:57:57,700 --> 00:58:00,600
救命啊！  雷恩
Help!  Ryan.

957
00:58:00,670 --> 00:58:02,660
救救我！爸！
Help! Dad!

958
00:58:02,740 --> 00:58:05,800
雷恩  爸，快来救我！
Ryan.  Dad! Help me!

959
00:58:15,320 --> 00:58:16,750
什么？
What?

960
00:58:19,050 --> 00:58:21,040
等等，什么？等等，什么？
Wait! What? What? Wait!

961
00:58:21,120 --> 00:58:23,390
等等…等等…
Wait, wait, wait, wait! Hey! Hey! Hey!

962
00:58:26,790 --> 00:58:27,920
放开我
Get off me!

963
00:58:28,660 --> 00:58:30,060
这是怎么回事？
What is goin' on here?

964
00:58:30,130 --> 00:58:34,160
米田共不会说话 只会像球一样乱滚
Stinky does not speak.  It rolls like a little ball.

965
00:58:34,240 --> 00:58:36,030
慢着，你们以为我是…
Wait. You guys think I'm a...?

966
00:58:36,100 --> 00:58:39,130
闭嘴，米田共  别说话，快滚吧
Achtung, Stinky!  Less talk, more roll.

967
00:58:39,210 --> 00:58:41,170
好  翻滚吧
Ja.  Roll! Roll!

968
00:58:41,240 --> 00:58:43,340
搞什么？
What the...? Hey!

969
00:58:43,410 --> 00:58:46,070
滚米田共能让屁股结实
Rolling the dung is good for tight buns!

970
00:58:46,150 --> 00:58:48,210
我就让你们滚蛋吧
I'll give you something to roll about!

971
00:58:51,750 --> 00:58:54,150
幸好BJ没看到这一幕
It's a good thing Bridget didn't see that!

972
00:58:54,220 --> 00:58:57,210
BJ？赖瑞？ 他们都不见了
Bridget? Larry! They're gone.

973
00:58:58,290 --> 00:58:59,520
我得找到他们
I gotta find them!

974
00:58:59,590 --> 00:59:02,190
不，我得先找到山大王
No! I gotta find Samson first!

975
00:59:02,260 --> 00:59:03,730
不，先找到…
No! First...

976
00:59:08,040 --> 00:59:10,090
山大王，山大王！
Sam. Sam!

977
00:59:22,820 --> 00:59:24,410
BJ！赖瑞！
Bridget! Larry!

978
00:59:24,490 --> 00:59:26,250
雷恩，你还活着
Oh, Ryan! You're alive!

979
00:59:26,320 --> 00:59:28,310
真高兴见到你们
Good to see you guys.

980
00:59:28,390 --> 00:59:30,860
给我抱抱  赖瑞
Where's my hug?  Larry.

981
00:59:30,920 --> 00:59:33,690
来吧  我也很高兴见到你
There it is.  It's good to see you too.

982
00:59:35,460 --> 00:59:37,120
你们跑来这儿干吗？
What are you guys doing here?

983
00:59:37,200 --> 00:59:39,460
我们跟你爸一起来找你
We came here with your father to find you.

984
00:59:39,530 --> 00:59:43,030
他大概正在外头找我们
And he's probably out there right now lookin' for us.

985
00:59:44,200 --> 00:59:46,000
我也希望是这样
I wish he were.

986
00:59:46,070 --> 00:59:48,840
不过牛羚把他撞下悬崖
But some of these wildebeests pushed him off a cliff.

987
00:59:48,910 --> 00:59:50,470
什么？  什么？
What?  What?

988
00:59:50,540 --> 00:59:53,950
我想他活不成了 他没救了
I don't think he made it. I don't see how he could.

989
00:59:54,010 --> 00:59:55,910
噢，雷恩
Oh, Ryan.

990
00:59:55,980 --> 00:59:58,250
很抱歉害你们落到这个下场
I'm sorry I got you into this.

991
00:59:58,320 --> 01:00:02,050
蛮牛，你一定会很喜欢 我们带给你的东西
Kazar, I think you'll be very pleased with what I brought you.

992
01:00:02,120 --> 01:00:04,590
这是什么？ 另一头狮子呢？
What's this? Where's the other lion?

993
01:00:04,660 --> 01:00:08,360
对，我正要告诉你 那里有一座悬崖
Right. Well, I was gonna tell you, there was this cliff and...

994
01:00:09,830 --> 01:00:12,700
你干吗用这种眼神看我？
Why are you looking at me like that?

995
01:00:12,770 --> 01:00:16,500
这是你今天第二次凸槌了 布雷
That's twice you've been out of step today, Blag!

996
01:00:16,570 --> 01:00:17,830
你这大笨蛋
You klutz.

997
01:00:17,910 --> 01:00:20,570
你明明知道 如果不吃掉狮子
You know we can't ascend to the top of the food chain

998
01:00:20,640 --> 01:00:23,700
就升不上食物链顶端
until we eat a lion!

999
01:00:25,350 --> 01:00:28,340
不过至少我可以
Well, at least there'll be enough for my ascension.

1000
01:00:28,420 --> 01:00:29,940
那我们怎么办？
What about the rest of us?

1001
01:00:30,020 --> 01:00:32,850
向前踢、向侧踢
Step-kick, pivot-kick!

1002
01:00:38,330 --> 01:00:40,490
好痛哦，我扭伤了脚
Ouch! I twisted a hoof!

1003
01:00:40,560 --> 01:00:43,720
你为他们辛苦为他们忙 他们却伤透了你的心
You work and you work. Then they break your heart.

1004
01:00:43,800 --> 01:00:48,130
我的演艺事业完了  准备祭品
There goes my career!  Prepare the sacrifices!

1005
01:00:51,370 --> 01:00:53,640
我为什么让他自己去呢？
Why did I let him go off by himself?

1006
01:00:53,710 --> 01:00:57,800
他连蚊子都抓不到 更别说是午餐了
He couldn't catch a cold, much less his own lunch.

1007
01:00:59,410 --> 01:01:01,010
不过我抓得到你
Bet I could catch you.

1008
01:01:01,080 --> 01:01:02,410
拜托
Please.

1009
01:01:02,480 --> 01:01:05,610
我的天敌是汽车…什么？
My natural predator is fuel inject... What?

1010
01:01:05,690 --> 01:01:08,950
我就知道你没有死 我就知道
I knew you weren't really gone. I knew it!

1011
01:01:09,020 --> 01:01:12,360
我早就料到了 咱们还是麻吉，对吧？
Come on, I knew it! We're still buddies, right?

1012
01:01:13,690 --> 01:01:15,290
我失去了雷恩
I lost Ryan.

1013
01:01:15,360 --> 01:01:18,660
太多敌人了 他被他们抓走了
There were too many. They just took him.

1014
01:01:18,730 --> 01:01:21,390
谁？谁把他抓走？
Who? Who took him?

1015
01:01:21,470 --> 01:01:25,030
牛羚  那些有蹄的怪胎
Wildebeests.  The freaks with the hooves!

1016
01:01:25,110 --> 01:01:26,970
他们也把赖瑞和BJ抓走
They got Larry and Bridget too.

1017
01:01:27,040 --> 01:01:30,310
我打不过他们…
Couldn't fight, couldn't...

1018
01:01:30,380 --> 01:01:31,970
加油，山大王，你是狮子耶
Come on, Sam. You're a lion.

1019
01:01:32,050 --> 01:01:34,170
你是万兽之王的后代
You come from a long line of kings.

1020
01:01:34,250 --> 01:01:36,510
没错 也许你不是来自大草原
Yeah, maybe you're not from the wild.

1021
01:01:36,580 --> 01:01:38,570
但是你拥有神鬼战士的血统
But fighting's in your blood!

1022
01:01:38,650 --> 01:01:42,090
不，我永远不会是真正的狮子
No. I'll never be a real lion.

1023
01:01:42,160 --> 01:01:45,060
错了，你是一头真正的狮子
Wrong! You are a real lion.

1024
01:01:45,130 --> 01:01:47,030
不管你来自哪里
Doesn't matter where you're from:

1025
01:01:47,090 --> 01:01:49,930
动物园、丛林、金鱼缸
Zoo, jungle, goldfish bowl.

1026
01:01:50,000 --> 01:01:51,930
内心的勇气才重要
It's what's in here.

1027
01:01:52,000 --> 01:01:54,300
你的心决定你是谁
That determines who you are!

1028
01:01:54,370 --> 01:01:56,860
至少你都是这么跟你儿子说的
At least, that's what you always told your son.

1029
01:01:56,940 --> 01:01:59,430
现在他被抓住了
Now he's out there, Sammy,

1030
01:01:59,510 --> 01:02:02,530
而且他需要你
and he needs you.

1031
01:02:02,610 --> 01:02:05,130
还有谁能教他怎么吼？
Who else is gonna teach him how to roar?

1032
01:02:09,550 --> 01:02:10,950
这就对了，山大王
That's it, Sammy.

1033
01:02:16,320 --> 01:02:17,590
很好
That's it.

1034
01:02:23,160 --> 01:02:26,890
我们去找我儿子和我的朋友
Let's go find my son... and my friends.

1035
01:02:26,970 --> 01:02:29,560
好耶，什么都阻止不了我们
Yeah! Nothing's gonna stop us!

1036
01:02:29,640 --> 01:02:33,040
只是我们根本不知道 我们要去哪里
Except that we have no idea where we're going!

1037
01:02:34,140 --> 01:02:35,800
跟随你的直觉
Follow your instincts.

1038
01:02:35,880 --> 01:02:37,540
跟随你的直觉
Follow your instincts.

1039
01:02:37,610 --> 01:02:41,880
那是什么？  我的…直觉
What is that?  My... instincts?

1040
01:02:45,820 --> 01:02:48,450
斑尼？  就快到了
Benny?  You're almost there.

1041
01:02:49,860 --> 01:02:51,120
我终于搞懂了
That settles it, then.

1042
01:02:51,190 --> 01:02:54,850
我妈怀我的时候 一定是喝了太多泳池的水
My mother definitely drank pool water when she was pregnant with me.

1043
01:02:54,930 --> 01:02:56,450
斑尼，你看
Benny, look.

1044
01:02:56,530 --> 01:02:58,900
有蹄的怪胎
The freaks with hooves!

1045
01:02:58,970 --> 01:03:00,300
雷恩在那里面
Ryan's in there.

1046
01:03:01,540 --> 01:03:03,730
你不能直接闯进去 那等于是自杀
You can't just barge in. That's suicide!

1047
01:03:03,800 --> 01:03:07,330
斑尼，让开  别听那个鼠辈的话
Benny, get out of my way!  Don't listen to the rat.

1048
01:03:07,410 --> 01:03:10,400
喂，你骂谁鼠辈？  当然是你罗
Hey, who are you calling a rat?  You, of course.

1049
01:03:10,480 --> 01:03:13,940
你会曝露我们的位置  小心我告你哦
You'll give away our position.  I'll have you written up for that!

1050
01:03:14,010 --> 01:03:17,210
猪头，你搞砸了我们的伪装 弟兄们！分散！
Fool! You blew our cover! Men! Scatter!

1051
01:03:18,250 --> 01:03:20,410
别跑得那么快
Not so fast!

1052
01:03:20,490 --> 01:03:23,920
你看我抓到谁，山大老 这是你的狮子本能
Look who I got, Sammy. It's your lion instincts.

1053
01:03:23,990 --> 01:03:25,360
你们是谁？
Who are you guys?

1054
01:03:25,430 --> 01:03:28,120
我们是谁不重要  我是斗篷，他是迷彩
Our names aren't important.  I'm Cloak. He's Camo.

1055
01:03:28,200 --> 01:03:31,360
我们是卧底探员  你们为什么一直误导我？
We're covert agents.  Why have you been leading me around?

1056
01:03:31,430 --> 01:03:33,800
这是机密情报  最高机密
That's classified.  Top-secret.

1057
01:03:33,870 --> 01:03:35,960
那些牛羚发疯了  斗篷
The wildebeests have gone mad.  Cloak.

1058
01:03:36,040 --> 01:03:39,470
我又没告诉他们 我们打算利用他们打败蛮牛…
It's not like I told them our plan is to use them to defeat Kazar's...

1059
01:03:39,540 --> 01:03:42,370
听好，告诉我 他们把我儿子抓去了吗？
Listen, just tell me, did they take my son in there?

1060
01:03:42,440 --> 01:03:44,240
我不能说 你 一定要说
That's need-to-know.  They did.

1061
01:03:44,310 --> 01:03:47,540
他们以为那只无尾熊是神兽  你是史上最逊的卧底探员
They think the koala's a god.  You're the worst covert agent!

1062
01:03:47,610 --> 01:03:50,050
是吗？ 那我怎么会这一招？弟兄们！
Oh, yeah? Then why can I do this? Men!

1063
01:03:50,120 --> 01:03:52,880
不，住手，山大王！
Hey! No! Stop! Sammy!

1064
01:03:52,950 --> 01:03:57,250
猪头，这一招是机密耶  这是秘密，这才是最高机密
Idiot! That maneuver's confidential.  It's secret. This one's confidential.

1065
01:03:57,320 --> 01:03:59,260
迷彩  这是机密情报
Cloak!  And this one's restricted.

1066
01:03:59,330 --> 01:04:03,130
超级机密情报 最高机密，超级超级机密
Super-secret. Top-secret. This is ultra-secret!

1067
01:04:03,200 --> 01:04:04,690
够了，别说了
Enough! No more!

1068
01:04:04,770 --> 01:04:08,390
让他们见识超级最高机密 「够了」的招式，没问题！
Show 'em the super-top-secret "no more?" Gotcha!

1069
01:04:08,470 --> 01:04:09,490
不！
No!

1070
01:04:11,340 --> 01:04:12,670
我有个点子
I got an idea.

1071
01:04:16,740 --> 01:04:19,580
神兽到底是谁呀？ 我来对付他
Who is this Great Him, anyway? I'll take him on.

1072
01:04:19,650 --> 01:04:22,050
我是女神兽 要让他尝尝我的厉害
I'm the Great Her! I'll show Him a thing or two.

1073
01:04:22,120 --> 01:04:24,550
我是天不怕地不怕的纽约客耶
I'm from New York City, for Pete's sake.

1074
01:04:25,620 --> 01:04:27,140
天啊
Oh, my.

1075
01:04:41,270 --> 01:04:43,630
这一定是在开玩笑
You have got to be kidding me.

1076
01:04:52,780 --> 01:04:55,510
尼啾，我不知道你在搞什么鬼
Nigel, I don't know what you're trying to pull,

1077
01:04:55,580 --> 01:04:57,640
不过我要海扁你…  住嘴
but I will kick your...  Silence!

1078
01:04:58,590 --> 01:05:00,640
你这小王八…
Why, you little...

1079
01:05:00,720 --> 01:05:02,420
我叫你住嘴
Silence, again!

1080
01:05:02,490 --> 01:05:05,890
你不能跟我说话
You do not speak to me!

1081
01:05:05,960 --> 01:05:07,390
尼啾，这是怎么回事？
Nigel, what's the deal?

1082
01:05:07,460 --> 01:05:10,400
伟大的神兽 可以准备举行晚宴了吗？
Great Him, shall we prepare the feast?

1083
01:05:10,460 --> 01:05:13,990
可以，我们要吃什么？
Yes, we shall! What's on the menu?

1084
01:05:14,070 --> 01:05:15,470
他们
Them.

1085
01:05:16,600 --> 01:05:18,130
噢，不
Oh, no.

1086
01:05:18,210 --> 01:05:20,870
吃朋友就能当神兽 不吃朋友的话…
Eat friends and be god, don't eat friends...

1087
01:05:20,940 --> 01:05:23,270
神兽、朋友，神兽、朋友…
God, friends, god, friends. God, I...

1088
01:05:23,340 --> 01:05:24,940
真是令人左右为难
Well, that was subtle.

1089
01:05:25,010 --> 01:05:26,170
准备升火烤肉
Prepare the meat fire!

1090
01:05:29,850 --> 01:05:31,410
等等
Wait!

1091
01:05:33,350 --> 01:05:36,620
烤肉不能没有
We cannot cook them without...

1092
01:05:38,060 --> 01:05:39,150
…洋葱
...onion!

1093
01:05:39,230 --> 01:05:42,680
洋葱…洋葱…
Onions. Onions. Onions.

1094
01:05:43,900 --> 01:05:45,800
哇塞，好快哦
Well, that was fast.

1095
01:05:45,870 --> 01:05:47,990
开始举行仪式
Let the ritual begin.

1096
01:05:52,110 --> 01:05:53,440
走吧
Move it!

1097
01:05:53,510 --> 01:05:55,810
我对你超不爽的
I am so mad at you!

1098
01:05:56,940 --> 01:06:01,180
等等，我们也需要…帽子
Wait! We also need... hats!

1099
01:06:02,650 --> 01:06:06,280
我们没有死刑的派对帽吗？
Do we not have the party hats of death?

1100
01:06:06,350 --> 01:06:07,910
我有呀
I've got mine!

1101
01:06:07,990 --> 01:06:11,650
而且宴会开始之前 我们都要…
And before the feast, we must all...

1102
01:06:12,060 --> 01:06:13,650
搞什么？
What the...?

1103
01:06:14,530 --> 01:06:15,760
飘浮
...levitate...

1104
01:06:15,830 --> 01:06:17,690
发疯似的旋转
...and spin uncontrollably!

1105
01:06:17,760 --> 01:06:20,360
觉得有点想吐
And feel a bit sick.

1106
01:06:21,270 --> 01:06:22,600
这玩意要怎么停下来呀？
How do I stop this thing?

1107
01:06:22,670 --> 01:06:24,400
大伙儿  斑尼？
Guys.  Benny?

1108
01:06:24,470 --> 01:06:26,500
看，一只松鼠  赖瑞
Look, a squirrel!  Larry!

1109
01:06:27,410 --> 01:06:29,340
我们有个计划，跟我来
We've got a plan. Follow me.

1110
01:06:29,410 --> 01:06:32,000
我们？  我会飞
We?  I can fly!

1111
01:06:32,080 --> 01:06:35,540
伟大的神兽 我们臣服在你的威力之下
Oh, Great Him, we are humbled by your power.

1112
01:06:35,620 --> 01:06:39,480
臣服吧 只有神兽才会这一招
Be humbled. Only the Great Him can do this!

1113
01:06:41,960 --> 01:06:44,080
火山热气  我们的伪装被识破了
Volcanic gas!  Our cover's blown!

1114
01:06:44,160 --> 01:06:46,650
严重故障，弃船！
Major malfunction! Abandon ship!

1115
01:06:55,240 --> 01:06:58,640
天啊  你也该赶来了
Oh, boy.  Well, about time you got here.

1116
01:06:58,710 --> 01:07:01,370
伟大的神兽 这又是另一个奇迹
Great Him, it's another miracle!

1117
01:07:01,440 --> 01:07:04,640
你把真正的狮子带来
You've delivered us a real lion!

1118
01:07:04,710 --> 01:07:06,840
布雷，你出运了
Blag, your luck has turned.

1119
01:07:06,910 --> 01:07:11,250
多亏伟大神兽的帮忙 我们都会升级到食物链顶端
Thanks to the Great Him, we shall all ascend tonight.

1120
01:07:11,320 --> 01:07:14,310
尼啾，我们得声东击西
Nigel, we've got to create a distraction.

1121
01:07:15,220 --> 01:07:16,520
等一下
Hang on a sec!

1122
01:07:16,590 --> 01:07:19,250
我袖里乾坤，藏了一大堆奇迹
I've got miracles comin' out my ears!

1123
01:07:19,330 --> 01:07:22,490
预备，退后
Ready? Stand back...

1124
01:07:22,560 --> 01:07:26,160
伟大的神兽要对付
...as the Great Me attacks the lion

1125
01:07:26,230 --> 01:07:29,760
比我大73倍的狮子
over 73 times my size!

1126
01:07:33,510 --> 01:07:36,670
爸？我爸还活着！ 大伙儿，我爸没有死
Dad? My dad's alive! Guys, my dad made it!

1127
01:07:36,740 --> 01:07:38,540
雷恩，不！  快点，我要去找他
Ryan, no!  Hurry, I got to see him!

1128
01:07:42,480 --> 01:07:43,950
打呀，打呀
Whack, whack, whack!

1129
01:07:44,020 --> 01:07:45,420
爸！  什么？雷恩！
Dad!  What? Ryan!

1130
01:07:47,020 --> 01:07:49,780
这是我的伎俩  雷恩，不！
I planned this.  Ryan, no!

1131
01:07:54,630 --> 01:07:57,860
宇宙秩序终于逆转了
At long last, the cosmic balance has shifted.

1132
01:07:57,930 --> 01:08:00,730
跟紧我 猎物变成掠食动物
Stay close.  Prey has become predator!

1133
01:08:00,800 --> 01:08:02,700
掠食动物变成猎物
And predator has become prey!

1134
01:08:02,770 --> 01:08:05,400
草食动物终于打败肉食动物
And the hoof finally trumps the claw!

1135
01:08:05,540 --> 01:08:08,300
爸，来吧 让我们教训这些牛肉干
Come on, Dad! Let's show these turkey-jerkies

1136
01:08:08,380 --> 01:08:10,500
让他们知道谁才是老大
who's at the top of the food chain!

1137
01:08:12,310 --> 01:08:14,780
先把小狮子吃掉
Let's eat the brat first.

1138
01:08:15,120 --> 01:08:18,110
想都别想
Over my dead body!

1139
01:08:31,930 --> 01:08:33,560
好耶
Yeah.

1140
01:08:35,100 --> 01:08:36,690
爸！
Dad!

1141
01:08:40,170 --> 01:08:42,800
我们不想办法 他就会把山大王杀死
He's gonna kill Samson if we don't do something!

1142
01:08:42,880 --> 01:08:45,570
咱们何不使用秘密绝招？
Why don't we use the secret play?

1143
01:08:45,650 --> 01:08:49,410
我知道 赖瑞，闭嘴，那太蠢了
I know. Shut up, Larry. That's stupid.

1144
01:08:49,480 --> 01:08:51,810
不，那太聪明了
No! It's brilliant!

1145
01:08:51,890 --> 01:08:54,650
当我提到预兆他们就笑我
They laughed at me when I spoke of the Omen.

1146
01:08:54,720 --> 01:08:58,350
看看现在谁还敢笑
But look who's laughing now!

1147
01:09:03,900 --> 01:09:06,760
左边一点，好 不对，右边一点
Little to the left. Yeah. No! Little to the right!

1148
01:09:06,830 --> 01:09:09,600
下一层 食物链最底端
Next floor: Bottom of the food chain!

1149
01:09:09,840 --> 01:09:11,240
叮！
Ding!

1150
01:09:12,110 --> 01:09:13,300
发射！
Fire!

1151
01:09:20,580 --> 01:09:23,240
我得找更大的武器
We gotta find something bigger!

1152
01:09:23,320 --> 01:09:25,780
我知道哪里有更大的武器
I know where we can find something bigger.

1153
01:09:29,520 --> 01:09:31,820
预备，雷恩  拉紧一点
Ready, Ryan?  Dig deep!

1154
01:09:31,890 --> 01:09:33,520
你应该待在家里
You should have stayed at home.

1155
01:09:33,590 --> 01:09:36,860
咱们的祭坛会是你的坟墓
Now our shrine will become your tomb.

1156
01:09:36,930 --> 01:09:38,300
发射
Fire!

1157
01:09:45,670 --> 01:09:47,540
雷恩！
Ryan!

1158
01:09:48,910 --> 01:09:49,900
雷恩！
Ryan!

1159
01:09:51,880 --> 01:09:53,970
通常在上主菜之前
I don't typically eat dessert

1160
01:09:54,050 --> 01:09:56,170
我不会先吃甜点
before the main course!

1161
01:09:56,680 --> 01:09:59,280
离我儿子远一点
Get away from my son!

1162
01:10:08,730 --> 01:10:09,890
雷恩
Ryan.

1163
01:10:16,500 --> 01:10:19,700
雷恩，你没事吧？
Ryan, are you still with me?

1164
01:10:19,770 --> 01:10:23,970
我没事，我只想告诉你
It's OK, Dad. I just want you to know

1165
01:10:24,040 --> 01:10:28,610
很遗憾你不像我 有一个好父亲
I'm sorry you didn't have a father like the one I have.

1166
01:10:28,680 --> 01:10:30,340
雷恩
Ryan.

1167
01:10:33,020 --> 01:10:34,850
好感人哦
How touching.

1168
01:10:34,920 --> 01:10:37,750
不过临终遗言通常都很感人
But then, last words usually are.

1169
01:10:39,930 --> 01:10:41,150
解决他们
Finish them.

1170
01:10:50,040 --> 01:10:51,590
你们在干吗？
What are you doing?

1171
01:10:51,670 --> 01:10:55,470
我命令你们攻击他们 就像真正的掠食动物那样
I command you to attack them, like true predators!

1172
01:10:55,540 --> 01:10:58,880
我们不是掠食动物 不想再假装下去
We're tired of pretending to be something we're not.

1173
01:10:58,950 --> 01:11:03,080
更重要的是，我们受够你了
But most of all, we're tired of you.

1174
01:11:06,420 --> 01:11:09,010
布雷，好吧
Blag. Fine.

1175
01:11:09,090 --> 01:11:10,990
那我就亲手杀死他们
I'll kill them myself!

1176
01:11:16,530 --> 01:11:20,020
爸，记得你在故事里 总是告诉我
Dad, remember what you always told me in your stories:

1177
01:11:20,100 --> 01:11:21,500
鼓起勇气
Dig deep.

1178
01:11:40,150 --> 01:11:43,020
好耶，宝贝
Oh, yeah, baby!

1179
01:12:05,080 --> 01:12:06,410
我们走吧
Let's go.

1180
01:12:06,480 --> 01:12:08,570
好
Yeah.

1181
01:12:08,650 --> 01:12:11,210
来吧，我们离开这鬼地方  快走吧
Come on, let's get out of here!  Get out of here!

1182
01:12:11,280 --> 01:12:14,980
我要在大家面前说 我一直都讨厌你编的舞
And for the record, I've always hated your choreography.

1183
01:12:15,060 --> 01:12:17,890
真的很…俗耶
It's so... '80s.

1184
01:12:19,890 --> 01:12:21,290
没错，跑吧
That's right! Run!

1185
01:12:21,360 --> 01:12:23,890
就像胆小的猎物逃跑吧
Run like the cowardly prey that you are!

1186
01:12:23,960 --> 01:12:25,950
我会猎杀你们
I will hunt you down!

1187
01:12:28,370 --> 01:12:30,200
大伙儿，快到船上
Everyone! To the boat!

1188
01:12:30,270 --> 01:12:32,030
食物链的顶端，妈！
Top of the food chain, Ma!

1189
01:12:32,110 --> 01:12:35,400
食物链的顶端…
Top of the food chain...

1190
01:12:35,480 --> 01:12:39,410
我是小可爱，我爱你 我是小可爱，我爱你
I'm so cuddly! I like you! I'm so cuddly! I like you!

1191
01:12:39,480 --> 01:12:41,810
我是小可爱，我爱你 我是小可爱
I'm so cuddly! I like you! I'm so cuddly!

1192
01:12:50,460 --> 01:12:52,760
快点，不然就逃不了
Hurry! We're never gonna make it!

1193
01:12:52,830 --> 01:12:55,560
用力推，毛绒绒的怪胎，快推
Push, you crazy, hairy monsters! Push!

1194
01:12:56,660 --> 01:12:59,960
赖瑞，打倒档  倒档
Larry, throw it in reverse!  Reverse throwing!

1195
01:13:11,440 --> 01:13:14,970
至少我在大草原消失前 目睹这一切
At least I saw the wild before it disappeared.

1196
01:13:15,050 --> 01:13:17,540
我还是看得到它，它就在…
I can still see it. It's right...

1197
01:13:17,620 --> 01:13:20,550
我的心中 我找到我的吼声
Here. I found my roar.

1198
01:13:21,090 --> 01:13:23,610
我们都找到了，儿子
We both did, son.

1199
01:13:24,320 --> 01:13:28,690
爸，这是我们第一个 「山大王和雷恩」的故事
You know, Dad, this'll be our first story of Samson and Ryan the Wild.

1200
01:13:28,760 --> 01:13:31,030
我想不会有人相信吧
I don't think anybody's gonna believe it.

1201
01:13:33,970 --> 01:13:35,940
炸弹来袭
Incoming!

1202
01:13:41,140 --> 01:13:43,270
我是小可爱
I'm so cuddly!

1203
01:13:43,340 --> 01:13:46,470
我是小可爱
Cuddly! I'm so cuddly!

1204
01:13:46,550 --> 01:13:49,540
我知道你很可爱 可是你会飘浮吗？
I know you're cuddly. But can you float?

1205
01:13:52,490 --> 01:13:54,540
今天真是个 美好的一天
I'm having a  Really nice day

1206
01:13:54,620 --> 01:13:56,490
美好的一天 美好的一天
Really nice day Really nice day

1207
01:13:56,560 --> 01:13:58,490
向左踢
Step-kick left!

1208
01:13:58,560 --> 01:14:00,250
美好的一天
Really nice day

1209
01:14:00,330 --> 01:14:01,320
向右踢
Step-kick right!

1210
01:14:02,630 --> 01:14:05,030
非常好  不，棒呆了
Splendid.  No! Smashing. Hey!

1211
01:14:05,100 --> 01:14:07,500
超厉害的  你们真的觉得很棒吗？
Stupendous!  Are you guys sure about this?

1212
01:14:07,570 --> 01:14:09,760
脱胎换骨行动已经完成
Operation Snake-Over is now complete.

1213
01:14:09,840 --> 01:14:12,700
大伙儿看，我是秘密情报员
Hey, look, everyone! I'm a secret agent!

1214
01:14:14,470 --> 01:14:17,500
BJ，我知道啦 你不只是身材高挑的女神
Bridget, I get it. You're more than a tall, lanky goddess.

1215
01:14:17,580 --> 01:14:19,640
也是坚强独立的女性
